n%20apply%20to%20other%20elements%20of%20life%20as%20well%2C%20such%20as%20income%2C%20work%2C%20food%20ingredients%2C%20cosmetic%20products%20and%20medicines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2017%2C%20an%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20in%20Lucknow%20against%20the%20Halal%20India%20Private%20Limited%20Chennai%2C%20Jamiat%20Ulama-i-Hind%20Halal%20Trust%20Delhi%2C%20Halal%20Council%20of%20India%20Mumbai%20and%20Jamiat%20Ulama%20Maharashtra%20on%20charges%20of%20allegedly%20issuing%20halal%20certificates%20for%20some%20products%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20forged%20documents%20to%20exploit%20the%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20customers%20of%20a%20particular%20community%20(Muslims)%20for%20financial%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20these%20organisations%2C%20the%20FIR%20lists%20as%20accused%20other%20unknown%20manufacturing%20companies%20and%20their%20managers%20and%20owners%3B%20others%20involved%20in%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%3B%20others%20who%20are%20%E2%80%9Cfunding%20notified%20terrorist%20organisations%20and%20organisations%20involved%20in%20anti-national%20activities%E2%80%9D%20and%20people%20who%20are%20%E2%80%9Cconspiring%20to%20incite%20large-scale%20riots%20by%20messing%20with%20public%20faith.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20at%20the%20Hazratganj%20Police%20Station%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20one%20Shailendra%20Kumar%20Sharma%2C%20who%20accused%20these%20companies%20of%20issuing%20halal%20certificates%20without%20any%20authority%20for%20some%20products%20to%20increase%20their%20sales.%20Sharma%20said%20the%20companies%20allegedly%20did%20not%20follow%20prescribed%20standards%20while%20issuing%20these%20certificates%20and%20accused%20them%20of%20manipulating%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20to%20hurt%20the%20business%20and%20reduce%20the%20sales%20of%20those%20companies%20which%20had%20not%20received%20these%20certificates%2C%20Sharma%20alleged.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20criminal%20act%20and%20I%20suspect%20that%20these%20undue%20profits%20are%20being%20sent%20to%20anti-social%20and%20anti-national%20elements%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20invoked%20charges%20including%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20groups%2C%20extortion%2C%20uttering%20words%2C%20etc.%2C%20with%20deliberate%20intent%20to%20wound%20religious%20feelings%2C%20cheating%2C%20forgery%20of%20valuable%20security%2C%20forgery%20for%20purpose%20of%20cheating%20and%20using%20as%20genuine%20a%20forged%20document%20or%20electronic%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20the%20FIR%20was%20lodged%2C%20the%20state%20Food%20Security%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20(FSDA)%20department%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20under%20the%20direct%20ministerial%20control%20of%20Adityanath%20%E2%80%93%20on%20November%2018%20issued%20an%20order%20banning%20the%20manufacture%2C%20sale%2C%20storage%20and%20distribution%20of%20halal-certified%20products%20with%20immediate%20effect%20in%20the%20state%20from%20the%20view%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20health.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20Food%20products%20made%20for%20export%20were%2C%20however%2C%20excluded%20from%20this%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFSDA%20commissioner%20Anita%20Singh%20said%20that%20halal%20certification%20was%20being%20mentioned%20on%20the%20labels%20of%20certain%20food%20items%20such%20as%20dairy%20products%2C%20sugar%2C%20bakery%20items%2C%20peppermint%20oil%2C%20edible%20oils%20and%20salty%20ready-to-eat%20savouries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20the%20competent%20authorities%20mentioned%20in%20Section%2029%20of%20the%20Food%20Safety%20and%20Standards%20Act%2C%202006%2C%20have%20the%20right%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20food%20products%20and%20this%20is%20done%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20standards%20laid%20out%20in%20the%20law%2C%20said%20the%20commissioner%20in%20the%20order%20copy%20tweeted%20by%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20halal%20certification%20of%20food%20products%20was%20a%20parallel%20system%20which%20created%20a%20situation%20of%20confusion%2C%20and%20was%20completely%20against%20the%20basic%20intent%20of%20the%20said%20laws%2C%20said%20Singh.%20It%20was%20also%20punishable%20with%20a%20fine%20of%20upto%20Rs%203%20lakh%20under%20Section%2052%20of%20the%202006%20law%20for%20the%20offence%20of%20misbranding%20food%2C%20the%20UP%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamiat%20Ulama-i-Hind%20Halal%20Trust%20said%20the%20allegations%20levelled%20against%20it%20were%20%E2%80%9Cbaseless%E2%80%9D%20and%20aimed%20at%20%E2%80%9Ctarnishing%E2%80%9D%20its%20image.%C2%A0%20It%20would%20take%20necessary%20legal%20measures%20to%20counter%20the%20misinformation.%20The%20Jamiat%20said%20its%20certification%20process%20aligned%20with%20the%20requirement%20of%20manufacturers%20for%20both%20export%20and%20domestic%20distribution%20in%20India%2C%20and%20that%20it%20adhered%20to%20government%20regulations%20requiring%20all%20Halal%20Certification%20bodies%20to%20be%20registered%20by%20the%20National%20Accreditation%20Board%20for%20Certification%20Bodies%20under%20Quality%20Council%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20global%20demand%20for%20halal%20certified%20products%20is%20robust%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20imperative%20for%20Indian%20companies%20to%20obtain%20such%20certification%2C%20a%20fact%20endorsed%20by%20our%20Ministry%20of%20Commerce%2C%20Government%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jamiat%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCertain%20individuals%20propagating%20false%20claims%20against%20halal%20certification%20directly%20undermine%20our%20national%20interests%2C%20%E2%80%9D%20said%20Niaz%20A.%20Farooqui%2C%20CEO%2C%20Jamiat%20Ulama-i-Hind%20Halal%20Trust.%20He%20pointed%20out%20that%20halal%20trade%20stands%20as%20a%20significant%20%243.5%20trillion%20industry%2C%20and%20India%20benefits%20from%20its%20promotion%20in%20exports%20and%20tourism%2C%20particularly%20with%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20trade%20partners%20in%20the%20Organisation%20of%20Islamic%20Cooperation%20(OIC)%20countries%20and%20Southeast%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarooqui%20said%20the%20ban%20on%20halal%20certificate%20products%20in%20UP%20would%20impact%20the%20manufacturers%20and%20sellers%20of%20these%20products%20which%20cut%20across%20communities.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20about%20meat%20but%20other%20items%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHalal%20certification%20was%20not%20merely%20a%20requirement%20for%20importing%20countries%20but%20also%20for%20tourists%20visiting%20India%2C%20particularly%20those%20seeking%20halal%20certified%20products%20during%20their%20stay%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMufti%20Habeeb%20Yusuf%20Qasmi%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Halal%20Council%20of%20India%2C%20said%20the%20controversy%20over%20Halal%20had%20emerged%20because%20people%20had%20started%20viewing%20everything%20from%20the%20myopic%20approach%20of%20Hindu-Muslim.%20%E2%80%9CHalal%20is%20about%20hygiene%20and%20purity.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20matter%20of%20Hindu-Muslim%20but%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQasmi%20stressed%20that%20the%20misconceptions%20being%20spread%20over%20halal%20certificates%20were%20not%20in%20national%20interest%2C%20as%20these%20certifications%20promoted%20trade%2C%20especially%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20FIR%2C%20Sharma%20said%20halal%20certification%20was%20also%20found%20on%20%E2%80%9Cvegetarian%E2%80%9D%20items%20such%20as%20beauty%20products%2C%20oil%2C%20soap%2C%20toothpaste%20and%20honey%2C%20even%20though%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20such%20certifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20business%20interest%20of%20other%20communities%20was%20being%20hurt%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQasmi%20rejected%20the%20allegations%20that%20companies%20issuing%20halal%20certificates%20were%20trying%20to%20promote%20the%20businesses%20of%20only%20one%20community%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20others%20(read%20non-Muslims).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20absolutely%20false.%20Venky%E2%80%99s%2C%20Zorabian%20and%20Godrej%20(companies%20certified%20by%20the%20Halal%20Council%20of%20India)%20are%20all%20run%20by%20non-Muslims%2C%E2%80%9D%20Qasmi%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20stressing%20that%20Halal%20certification%20had%20in%20fact%20benefitted%20the%20businesses%20of%20non-Muslim%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQasmi%20said%20that%20the%20Halal%20certification%20was%20used%20for%20apparently%20vegetarian%20products%20as%20well%20in%20case%20they%20include%20animal%20products%20among%20their%20ingredients%20such%20as%20medicine%2C%20toothpaste%20and%20cosmetic%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarooqui%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20it%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20choice%20of%20individuals%20and%20manufacturers%20preferring%20to%20have%20certain%20certifications%20for%20their%20own%20satisfaction%20based%20upon%20the%20credentials%20of%20the%20certifying%20authorities.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20saves%20a%20large%20number%20of%20consumers%20from%20using%20products%20which%20they%20do%20not%20want%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons%20and%20ensures%20availability%20of%20need%20based%20products%20in%20the%20market.%20Those%20who%20do%20not%20want%20to%20use%20such%20products%20are%20free%20not%20to%20use%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamiat%E2%80%99s%20halal%20certificates%20are%20globally%20recognised%20by%20different%20governments%20and%20authorities%20all%20across%20the%20world%2C%20he%20added.%20These%20include%20Malaysia%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20Thailand%2C%20Singapore%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20Qatar%2C%20UAE%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700373190000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F21114815%2FFsNN-GdXgAEt_1x.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fups-crackdown-against-halal-products-a-criminal-case-and-a-ban%