p%3ERarely%20a%20month%20goes%20by%20without%20big%20tech%20companies%20getting%20fined%20for%20price%20fixing%2C%20squashing%20competitors%20or%20misusing%20data%2C%20but%20it%20can%20take%20years%20before%20they%20pay%20a%20penny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIreland's%20data%20regulator%20confirmed%20to%20AFP%20that%20Meta%20has%20not%20paid%20any%20of%20the%20two%20billion%20euros%20(%242.2%20billion)%20in%20fines%20issued%20since%20last%20September.%20TikTok%20also%20owes%20hundreds%20of%20millions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmazon%20is%20still%20appealing%20against%20a%20746%20million%20euro%20fine%20from%202021%2C%20Luxembourg's%20data%20regulator%20told%20AFP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%20is%20still%20disputing%20EU%20fines%20worth%20more%20than%20eight%20billion%20euros%20for%20abusing%20its%20market%20position%20between%202017%20and%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20has%20fought%20for%20years%20against%20a%20French%20antitrust%20fine%20of%201.1%20billion%20euros%20and%20an%20order%20to%20pay%2013%20billion%20euros%20of%20tax%20to%20Ireland.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20is%20constant%2C%20global%20and%20involves%20tech%20companies%20of%20all%20sizes%2C%20not%20just%20the%20big%20four.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20week%20Australia%20confirmed%20that%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20had%20not%20paid%20a%20fine%20imposed%20for%20failing%20to%20outline%20its%20plans%20to%20stamp%20out%20content%20depicting%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20--%20though%20X%20is%20now%20counter-suing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20say%20fining%20tech%20companies%20does%20not%20stop%20their%20bad%20behaviour%20and%20it%20is%20time%20for%20more%20drastic%20action.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMargarida%20Silva%2C%20a%20researcher%20at%20Dutch%20NGO%20the%20Centre%20for%20Research%20on%20Multinationals%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20tech%20firms%20have%20long%20revelled%20in%20their%20reputation%20for%20%26quot%3Bdisruption%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20paying%20the%20fines%20fits%20in%20with%20the%20way%20we've%20seen%20big%20tech%20companies%20challenge%20pretty%20much%20any%20enforcement%20of%20rules%20against%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Silva.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20the%20company%20ultimately%20loses%2C%20by%20that%20point%20they%20will%20have%20dragged%20the%20administration%20through%20years%20and%20years%20of%20expenditure.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20sets%20tech%20apart%20from%20industries%20like%20finance%2C%20she%20argued%2C%20where%20there%20is%20still%20an%20incentive%20to%20pay%20to%20reassure%20the%20public%20and%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Romain%20Rard%2C%20a%20lawyer%20at%20Gide%20Loyrette%20Nouel%20in%20Paris%2C%20said%20it%20was%20common%20sense%20that%20firms%20would%20look%20to%20appeal%20big%20penalties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20as%20if%20companies%20can%20just%20ignore%20the%20fine%2C%20challenge%20decisions%20and%20hope%20for%20the%20best%20that%20they%20can%20get%20away%20without%20having%20to%20pay%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20there%20have%20been%20notable%20successes%20for%20the%20companies%20--%20chip%20firms%20Intel%20and%20Qualcomm%20have%20both%20recently%20had%20billion-dollar%20EU%20antitrust%20fines%20overturned%20or%20dramatically%20reduced%20on%20appeal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEurope's%20system%20is%20different%20to%20jurisdictions%20like%20China%20or%20the%20United%20States%2C%20where%20fines%20often%20come%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20lengthy%20process%20and%20are%20announced%20as%20settlements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Facebook%20paid%20a%20record%20%245%20billion%20fine%20to%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%20(FTC)%20over%20the%20Cambridge%20Analytica%20scandal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20e-commerce%20giant%20Alibaba%20told%20investors%20in%202021%20it%20immediately%20paid%20a%20record%20almost%20%243%20billion%20fine%20to%20Chinese%20regulators%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActivists%20argue%20that%20these%20companies%20are%20simply%20too%20rich%20for%20financial%20penalties%20to%20have%20much%20impact.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustrian%20lawyer%20Max%20Schrems%2C%20who%20has%20campaigned%20vigorously%20for%20data%20rights%20in%20Europe%2C%20said%20the%20issue%20was%20exacerbated%20by%20uneven%20application%20of%20the%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Irish%20Data%20Protection%20Commission%2C%20he%20said%2C%20allowed%20the%20companies%20too%20much%20leeway%20with%20their%20appeals%20processes%20and%20issued%20fines%20that%20were%20far%20too%20small.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20AFP%2C%20Ireland's%20deputy%20data%20protection%20commissioner%20Graham%20Doyle%20defended%20his%20office's%20record%20and%20said%20fines%20were%20only%20one%20part%20of%20the%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20these%20investigations%20that%20we've%20finalised%2C%20whilst%20the%20fines%20tend%20to%20generate%20the%20most%20publicity%2C%20we%20have%20also%20imposed%20corrective%20measures%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20highlighted%20an%20investigation%20into%20Instagram%20for%20their%20handling%20of%20children's%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20405%20million%20euro%20fine%20is%20currently%20under%20appeal%2C%20but%20Doyle%20stressed%20that%20the%20platform%20had%20already%20fixed%20the%20initial%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActivists%20agree%20that%20fines%20can%20only%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESilva%20argued%20that%20rather%20than%20noodling%20around%20with%20financial%20penalties%2C%20it%20was%20time%20for%20competition%20regulators%20to%20step%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20urged%20them%20to%20halt%20future%20takeovers%20and%20mergers%20in%20the%20sector%20and%20undo%20the%20damage%20of%20the%20past%2C%20potentially%20even%20breaking%20up%20the%20companies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20of%20Meta%20would%20be%20entirely%20different%20if%20it%20hadn't%20been%20allowed%20to%20buy%20Instagram%20and%20WhatsApp%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAFP%20has%20asked%20Meta%20for%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700371440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F9aq0l6co_apple-google-meta-amazon_625x300_19_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-amazon-apple-google-meta-generated-billions-in-fines-but-didnt-pay-them-4586481%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rarely%20a%20month%20goes%20by%20without%20big%20tech%20companies%20getting%20fined%20for%20price%20fixing%2C%20squashing%20competitors%20or%20misusing%20data%2C%20but%20it%20can%20take%20years%20before%20they%20pay%20a%20penny.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-amazon-apple-google-meta-generated-billions-in-fines-but-didnt-pay-them-4586481%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-amazon-apple-google-meta-generated-billions-in-fines-but-didnt-pay-them-4586481%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-amazon-apple-google-meta-generated-billions-in-fines-but-didnt-pay-them-4586481%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Keen%20to%20get%20external%20investment%20for%20EV%20arm%20Switch%3A%20Ashok%20Leyland%20MD%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700371223000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-09%2F07%2Ffull%2F1694097244-3174.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fkeen-to-get-external-investment-for-ev-arm