80%99s%20activities%20were%20%E2%80%9Cprejudicial%20to%20the%20security%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20directed%20the%20administration%20to%20release%20Gul%20%E2%80%9Cforthwith%20from%20preventive%20custody%20if%20not%20required%20in%20any%20other%20case.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGul%20was%20already%20in%20police%20custody%20for%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20three%20FIRs%20filed%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20when%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20of%20Bandipora%20approved%20his%20detention%20(No.%2025%2FDMB%2FPSA%20of%202021-22)%20under%20the%20Public%20Safety%20Act%20on%20January%2014%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGul%20was%20consequently%20shifted%20to%20Central%20Jail%2C%20Jammu%2C%20some%20350%20km%20from%20his%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20quashing%20the%20PSA%20proceedings%20on%20November%209%2C%20the%20bench%20observed%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctendency%E2%80%A6.%20to%20detain%20the%20critics%20of%20the%20policies%20or%20commissions%2Fomissions%20of%20the%20government%20machinery%2C%20as%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20present%20detenu%E2%80%93%20a%20professional%20media%20person%2C%20%E2%80%A6%20is%20an%20abuse%20of%20the%20preventive%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F685272%2Fafter-nearly-2-years-jk-hc-grants-bail-to-kashmir-walla-editor-fahad-shah%2F%5C%22%3EAfter%20Nearly%202%20Years%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20HC%20Grants%20Bail%20to%20Kashmiri%20Journalist%20Fahad%20Shah%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20PSA%2C%20described%20by%20Amnesty%20International%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Clawless%20law%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20suspect%20can%20be%20detained%20without%20charges%20and%20put%20behind%20bars%20without%20trial%20for%20up%20to%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20ruled%20that%20the%20grounds%20of%20detention%20in%20Gul%E2%80%99s%20PSA%20dossier%20don%E2%80%99t%20indicate%20that%20he%20was%20involved%20in%20any%20wrongdoing.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20nowhere%20stated%20as%20to%20how%20the%20detenu%20had%20disrupted%20the%20public%20order%20creating%20any%20alleged%20enmity%2C%20inasmuch%20as%2C%20there%20is%20no%20specific%20instance%20in%20any%20of%20the%20allegations%20levelled%20against%20him%20to%20show%20that%20he%20had%20been%20working%20against%20the%20national%20interests.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20administration%2C%20without%20citing%20any%20instances%20in%20the%20PSA%20dossier%2C%20had%20termed%20Gul%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnegative%20critic%E2%80%9D%20who%20allegedly%20provoked%20people%20against%20the%20government%20policies%20through%20his%20tweets%20and%20news%20items%2C%20the%20bench%20observed%20that%20factual%20reporting%20by%20media%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20held%20against%20the%20journalists%20who%20report%20on%20such%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGul%20was%20working%20as%20a%20trainee%20reporter%20with%20the%20now%20defunct%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%20when%20he%20was%20detained%20under%20PSA%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20specific%20instance%20(in%20the%20PSA%20dossier)%20as%20to%20which%20of%20the%20posts%2Fwrite-ups%20(of%20Gul)%20are%20there%20as%20being%20so%20(create%20enmity%20against%20government)%20and%20on%20what%20date.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Nazir%20Ahmad%20Ronga%20and%20Tuba%20Manzoor%2C%20counsels%20for%20Gul%2C%20told%20the%20court%20that%20he%20could%20not%20make%20a%20meaningful%20representation%20against%20his%20detention%20as%20he%20was%20not%20provided%20the%20PSA%20dossier%2C%20FIRs%2C%20statements%20of%20witnesses%20and%20other%20documents%20which%20the%20authorities%20%E2%80%9Crelied%20upon%E2%80%9D%20to%20book%20him%20under%20the%20PSA%20%E2%80%9Cand%2C%20as%20such%2C%20(he)%20has%20been%20deprived%C2%A0%20of%20his%20constitutional%20and%20legal%20right.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%2C%20the%20court%20observed%20that%20the%20denial%20of%20documents%20to%20Gul%20and%20his%20continued%20detention%20%E2%80%9Cbecomes%20illegal%20and%20detention%20order%20has%20to%20be%20quashed%20on%20that%C2%A0ground%20alone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20absence%20of%20providing%20of%20the%20whole%20of%20the%20documentary%20record%2C%20the%20detenu%20cannot%20be%20said%20to%20be%20able%20to%20make%20an%20effective%20and%20meaningful%20representation%20against%20his%20detention%20which%20was%20his%20statutory%20as%20well%20as%20constitutional%20right%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20ruled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20a%20single%20bench%20of%20HC%20had%20dismissed%20a%20Habeas%C2%A0Corpus%20petition%20filed%20by%20Gul%20against%20his%20PSA%20detention%20order%20on%20December%201%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F649333%2Ffahad-shah-public-safety-act-jammu-kashmir-high-court%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Deprived%20of%20Rights%2C%20Non-Application%20of%20Mind%E2%80%99%3A%20J%26amp%3BK%20HC%20Tears%20Into%20PSA%20Proceedings%20Against%20Fahad%20Shah%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGul%20has%20also%20been%20booked%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20in%20FIR%20No%2012%2F2021%20filed%20by%20Hajin%20Police%20Station%20under%20Sections%20147%20(punishment%20for%20rioting)%2C%20336%20(endangering%20human%20life)%2C%20447%20(punishment%20for%20criminal%20trespassing)%2C%20and%20353%20(assaulting%20public%20servant)%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20an%20anti-encroachment%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%209%2C%202019%2C%20Gul%20reported%20that%20a%20local%20%3Cem%3Etehsildar%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20%E2%80%9Charassing%20and%20threatening%E2%80%9D%20locals%20while%20conducting%20anti-encroachment%20drive.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20the%20tehsildar%20allegedly%20targeted%20Gul%20and%20his%20relatives%E2%80%99%20houses%20in%20his%20native%20Shahgund%20village%20without%20serving%20any%20notice.%20This%20triggered%20protests%20and%20minor%20clashes%20between%20locals%20and%20officials%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hajin%20Police%20Station%20had%20booked%20Gul%20in%20a%20second%20case%20(FIR%20No%2079%2F2021)%20on%20October%2016%2C%202021%20under%20sections%20120-B%20(criminal%20conspiracy)%2C%20153-B%20(imputations%2C%20assertions%20prejudicial%20to%20national-integration)%20and%20505%20(public%20mischief)%20of%C2%A0the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20following%20his%20report%20on%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20local%20militant%20in%20Bandipora%E2%80%99s%20Gund%20Jahangeer%20village%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20accused%20him%20of%20%E2%80%9Cspreading%20false%20and%20fake%20narrative%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20anti-insurgency%20operation.%20However%2C%20a%20court%20granted%20him%20bail%20in%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20case%20(FIR%20No%2002%2F2022)%20against%20Gul%20was%20filed%20under%20sections%20147%2C%20148%20(armed%20with%20weapon%20that%20can%20cause%20death)%2C%20336%20%2C%20307%20(attempt%20to%20murder)%20and%20153-B%20(imputations%2C%20assertions%20prejudicial%20to%20national-integration)%20of%20the%20IPC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20filed%20after%20Gul%20posted%20a%20video%20clip%20on%20social%20media%20which%20showed%20some%20unidentified%20women%20shouting%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%20slogans%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20house%20of%20Saleem%20Parrey%2C%20a%20top%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20commander%2C%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20his%20killing%20in%20an%20encounter%20by%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20quashing%20of%20the%20PSA%20proceedings%20against%20Gul%20came%20ahead%20of%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20grant%20bail%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%20editor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F685272%2Fafter-nearly-2-years-jk-hc-grants-bail-to-kashmir-walla-editor-fahad-shah%2F%5C%22%3EFahad%20Shah%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20had%20been%20languishing%20in%20jail%20since%20February%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700370964000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F17202211%2FScreen-Shot-2022-01-17-at-8.21.54-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fjk-high-court-quashes-psa-proceedings-against-sajad-gul-rebukes-admin-for-not-applying-its-mind%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bench%20ruled%20that%20the%20grounds%20of%20detention%20in%20Gul's%20PSA%20dossier%20don%E2%80%99t%20indicate%20that%20he%20was%20involved%20in%20any%20wrongdoing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fjk-high-court-quashes-psa-proceedings-against-sajad-gul-rebukes-admin-for-not-applying-its-mind%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi's%20Air%20Quality%20Remains%20'Very%20Poor'%2C%20Schools%20To%20Reopen%20Tomorrow%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelhi%20continued%20to%20experience%20%26quot%3Bvery%20poor%26quot%3B%20air%20quality%20on%20Sunday%20morning%2C%20with%20an%20air%20quality%20index%20of%20398.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20System%20of%20Air%20Quality%20and%20Weather%20Forecasting%20And%20Research%20(SAFAR-India)%2C%20the%20AQI%20in%20Delhi%20was%20recorded%20at%20398%20at%207%3A15%20am%20on%20Sunday%2C%20categorising%20it%20as%20'very%20poor.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20data%20recorded%20at%208%20am%2C%20the%20AQI%20in%20Anand%20Vihar%20was%20336.%20Similarly%2C%20at%20Alipur%2C%20the%20AQI%20was%20recorded%20at%20363%2C%20at%20ITO%2C%20it%20was%20329%2C%20and%20at%20Bawana%2C%20it%20was%20recorded%20at%20371%20-%20all%20falling%20into%20the%20'very%20poor'%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20slight%20improvement%2C%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%20(CAQM)%20revoked%20Stage%20IV%20of%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP)%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20was%20prompted%20by%20the%20city's%20average%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20reaching%20319%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(CPCB).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Stage%20IV%20restrictions%20were%20lifted%2C%20Stages%20I%20to%20III%20of%20the%20GRAP%20will%20persist%20in%20the%20entire%20NCR%20to%20prevent%20AQI%20levels%20from%20worsening%20to%20the%20'Severe'%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20will%20come%20as%20a%20relief%20for%20students%20and%20parents%2C%20all%20government%20and%20private%20schools%20in%20Delhi%20will%20reopen%20from%20Monday%20following%20a%20decline%20in%20pollution%20levels.%20The%20announcement%20was%20made%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAQM%2C%20in%20a%20release%2C%20said%20that%20in%20view%20of%20the%20significant%20improvement%20in%20the%20average%20air%20quality%20of%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20the%20Sub-Committee%20for%20operationalization%20of%20actions%20under%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP)%20of%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%20in%20NCR%20and%20Adjoining%20Areas%20(CAQM)%20met%20today%20to%20review%20the%20current%20air%20quality%20scenario%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20comprehensively%20reviewing%20the%20overall%20air%20quality%20parameters%20of%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20the%20Sub-Committee%20observed%20that%20yesterday%20(i.e.%2C%20November%2017%2C%202023)%2C%20Delhi's%20average%20AQI%20clocked%20405%2C%20which%20started%20declining%20and%20showing%20improvement%20since%20the%20late%20evening%20of%20November%2017%2C%202023.%20Further%2C%20the%20air%20quality%20forecasts%20by%20IMD%2F%20IITM%20also%20do%20not%20indicate%20any%20steep%20degradation%20in%20the%20overall%20air%20quality%20of%20Delhi-NCR%20in%20the%20coming%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20release%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Central%20pollution%20watchdog%2C%20the%20present%20AQI%20level%20of%20Delhi%20is%20around%20322%20(very%20poor)%20recorded%20at%202%20pm%20on%20Saturday%2C%20which%20is%20about%20128%20AQI%20points%20below%20the%20threshold%20for%20invoking%20the%20GRAP%20Stage-IV%20actions%20and%20preventive%20actions%20under%20all%20Stages%20up%20to%20Stage-IV%20are%20underway%2C%20there%20is%20a%20likelihood%20of%20sustaining%20the%20improvement%20in%20AQI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20forecast%20by%20IMD%2FITM%20also%20does%20not%20indicate%20any%20further%20steep%20degradation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statutory%20body%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVarious%20agencies%20responsible%20for%20implementing%20measures%20under%20GRAP%20and%20Pollution%20Control%20Boards%20(PCBs)%20of%20NCR%20and%20DPCC%20have%20also%20been%20advised%20to%20ensure%20strict%20implementation%20and%20intensification%20of%20actions%20under%20Stage-I%2C%20Stage-II%20and%20Stage-III%20of%20the%20revised%20GRAP%20in%20the%20entire%20NCR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700370900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fslao08do_delhi-air-pollution-_625x300_03_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhis-air-quality-remains-very-poor-for-2nd-consecutive-day-4586395%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20continued%20to%20experience%20%26quot%3Bvery%20poor%26quot%3B%20air%20quality%20on%20Sunday%20morning%2C%20with%20an%20air%20quality%20index%20of%20398.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhis-air-quality-remains-very-poor-for-2nd-consecutive-day-4586395%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhis-air-quality-remains-very-poor-for-2nd-consecutive-day-4586395%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhis-air-quality-remains-very-poor-for-2nd-consecutive-day-4586395%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20to%20visit%20Texas%20as%20it%20prepares%20ne