3EAccording%20to%20a%20Channel%2012%20report%2C%20Israel%20has%20been%20insisting%20on%20keeping%20families%20together%20for%20any%20hostage%20deals.%20Hamas%20is%20being%20offered%20a%20pause%20in%20fighting%2C%20release%20of%20some%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20and%20the%20entry%20of%20more%20fuel%20into%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20now%20faces%20the%20dual%20pressure%20of%20domestic%20uproar%20over%20the%20failure%20to%20free%20the%20hostages%20so%20far%20and%20international%20concern%20over%20the%20massive%20human%20cost%20of%20its%20war%20in%20Gaza.%20Over%2011%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20Strip%20since%20the%20war%20broke%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700366460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fsugcitt8_gaza-war-pti_625x300_19_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbenjamin-netanyahu-israel-hamas-war-gaza-war-no-ceasfire-deal-yet-to-bring-israeli-hostages-home-benjamin-netanyahu-4586370%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22No%20deal%20has%20been%20reached%20yet%20for%20the%20release%20of%20hostages%20taken%20by%20Hamas%20during%20the%20October%207%20war%20that%20sparked%20the%20ongoing%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20both%20Israel%20and%20the%20US%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbenjamin-netanyahu-israel-hamas-war-gaza-war-no-ceasfire-deal-yet-to-bring-israeli-hostages-home-benjamin-netanyahu-4586370%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbenjamin-netanyahu-israel-hamas-war-gaza-war-no-ceasfire-deal-yet-to-bring-israeli-hostages-home-benjamin-netanyahu-4586370%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbenjamin-netanyahu-israel-hamas-war-gaza-war-no-ceasfire-deal-yet-to-bring-israeli-hostages-home-benjamin-netanyahu-4586370%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%2032