0look%20at%20the%20three%20key%20factors%20that%20give%20the%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20side%20an%20advantage%20over%20the%20Aussies%20in%20their%20quest%20for%20their%20third%20World%20Cup%20crown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Strong%20batting%20line-up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20dominance%20in%20the%20ongoing%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20their%20strong%20performances%20with%20the%20bat.%20The%20opening%20duo%20of%20Rohit%20Sharma%20(550%20runs)%20and%20Shubman%20Gill%20(350%20runs)%20have%20provided%20India%20with%20solid%20starts%20consistently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%2C%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20and%20KL%20Rahul%20have%20played%20pivotal%20roles%20in%20the%20middle-order%2C%20helping%20India%20post%20good%20totals%20like%20in%20the%20semi-final%20clash%20against%20New%20Zealand%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%2C%20with%20a%20tally%20of%20711%20runs%20in%2010%20matches%2C%20has%20established%20himself%20as%20the%20match-winner%20for%20India.%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20(526%20runs)%20has%20shown%20form%20with%20consecutive%20centuries%20against%20the%20Netherlands%20(128%20not%20out)%20and%20New%20Zealand%20(105).%20Meanwhile%2C%20KL%20Rahul%20(386%20runs)%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20backbone%20of%20the%20Indian%20batting%20line-up%2C%20showcasing%20remarkable%20temperament%20and%20calmness%20to%20steer%20India's%20chase%20effectively.%20If%20India%20has%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20the%20batting%20line-up%20must%20once%20again%20deliver%20a%20strong%20performance%20in%20the%20final%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Balanced%20bowling%20attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20famous%20saying%20goes%2C%20'Batters%20win%20you%20games%2C%20bowlers%20win%20you%20tournaments'%2C%20teams%20that%20have%20gone%20on%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Cups%20in%20the%20past%20boasted%20formidable%20and%20well-rounded%20bowling%20attacks.%20Whether%20it's%20the%20dominant%20West%20Indies%20team%20of%20the%201970s%20or%20the%20five-time%20champions%20Australia%2C%20a%20potent%20bowling%20unit%20has%20been%20a%20common%20link%20in%20their%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20Sharma%20too%20possesses%20a%20well-balanced%20bowling%20attack.%20Featuring%20the%20likes%20of%20Mohammed%20Shami%20(23%20wickets)%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20(18%20wickets)%2C%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20(16%20wickets)%2C%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20(15%20wickets)%20and%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20(13%20wickets)%2C%20India's%20bowling%20line-up%20is%20equipped%20to%20handle%20various%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20effectiveness%20of%20Indian%20bowlers%20has%20been%20evident%20on%20both%20the%20bouncy%2C%20swinging%20pitches%20of%20Dharamsala%20as%20well%20as%20the%20slow-turning%20tracks%20of%20Eden%20Gardens.%20A%20collective%20effort%20from%20the%20bowlers%20is%20a%20must%20if%20India%20aim%20to%20emerge%20victorious%20in%20Sunday's%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Multiple%20match-winners%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20cricket%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way%20and%20has%20witnessed%20a%20major%20evolution.%20From%20relying%20solely%20on%20the%20great%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%2C%20it%20has%20now%20evolved%20into%20a%20team%20of%20match-winners.%20Throughout%20the%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%2C%20India%20has%20witnessed%20the%20emergence%20of%20several%20match-winners%20in%20the%20course%20of%20their%2010-match%20unbeaten%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20opening%20clash%20against%20Australia%2C%20India%20found%20themselves%20in%20a%20precarious%20position%20at%202%2F3%2C%20only%20to%20be%20rescued%20by%20the%20combined%20efforts%20of%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20KL%20Rahul.%20In%20the%20match%20against%20New%20Zealand%20in%20Dharamsala%2C%20the%20Kiwis%20were%20cruising%20towards%20a%20formidable%20first%20innings%20total%2C%20propelled%20by%20Daryl%20Mitchell's%20century.%20However%2C%20a%20stellar%20performance%20by%20Mohammed%20Shami%20(5%2F54)%20altered%20the%20course%20of%20the%20game%2C%20causing%20New%20Zealand%20to%20collapse%20from%20178%2F3%20to%20273%20all-out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20encounter%20against%20South%20Africa%2C%20left-arm%20spinner%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20showcased%20his%20prowess%20by%20clinching%20figures%20of%205%2F33%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20India's%20resounding%20243-run%20victory.%20This%20reliance%20on%20different%20players%20augurs%20well%20for%20India%20going%20into%20the%20final%20in%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700364600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fkd4gm0r_virat-kohli-afp_625x300_17_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fcricket-world-cup-final-3-factors-that-give-india-the-edge-over-australia-4584779%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20dominance%20in%20the%20ongoing%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20the%20stellar%20performances%20of%20their%20batters%20throughout%20the%20tournament.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fcricket-world-cup-final-3-factors-that-give-india-the-edge-over-australia-4584779%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fcricket-world-cup-final-3-factors-that-give-india-the-edge-over-australia-4584779%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fcricket-world-cup-final-3-factors-that-give-india-the-edge-over-australia-4584779%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Old%20t-shirts%2C%20loo%20visits%20%26amp%3B%20other%20%E2%80%98totkas%E2%80%99%3A%20Quirks%20fans%20are%20following%20for%20WC%20final%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700363985000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105325246%2Cimgsize-350362.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fold-t-shirts-loo-visits-other-totkas-quirks-fans-are-following-for-wc-final%2Farticleshow%2F105324417.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20cricket%20fever%20grips%20Lucknow%20ahead%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%20final%2C%20fans%20are%20resorting%20to%20various%20superstitions%20in%20hopes%20of%20ensuring%20India's%20victory.%20Some%20are%20planning%20to%20wear%20lucky%20t-shirts%20or%20listen%20to%20the%20same%20song%20they%20heard%20during%20India's%20last%20World%20Cup%20win.%20Others%20have%20rituals%20like%20not%20checking%20the%20score%20on%20a%20particular%20website%20or%20only%20watching%20the%20last%2010%20overs%20of%20the%20match.%20These%20fans%20are%20determined%20to%20repeat%20the%20same%20actions%20that%20they%20believe%20brought%20luck%20in%20the%20past.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TNN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fold-t-shirts-loo-visits-other-totkas-quirks-fans-are-following-for-wc-final%2Farticleshow%2F105324417.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ahmedabad%20Weather%20And%20Pitch%20Report%3A%20Is%20Rain%20In%20Store%20For%20World%20Cup%20Final%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20day%20of%20reckoning%20for%20India%20and%20Australia%20as%20the%20two%20cricketing%20giants%20clash%20in%20Ahmedabad's%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20in%20the%20final%20of%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023.%20India%2C%20who%20are%20unbeaten%20in%20the%20competition%2C%20won%20all%209%20league%20matches%20before%20beating%20New%20Zealand%20to%20book%20their%20ticket%20to%20the%20final.%20Australia%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20suffered%20defeats%20in%20their%20opening%20two%20matches%20before%20winning%20the%20next%208%20on%20the%20bounce%20to%20set%20up%20a%20clash%20in%20the%20final%20with%20the%20hosts.%20As%20the%20two%20teams%20square%20off%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20the%20contest%20will%20not%20be%20limited%20to%20that%20between%20the%20bat%20and%20the%20ball.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAhmedabad%20Pitch%20Report%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EEver%20since%20the%20first%20semi-final%20between%20India%20and%20New%20Zealand%2C%20the%20pitch%20has%20been%20in%20focus.%20ICC's%20independent%20pitch%20consultant%20Andy%20Atkinson%20accused%20the%20BCCI%20of%20swapping%20the%20pitch%20in%20the%20last%20minute%20before%20the%20start%20of%20the%20semi-final.%20But%2C%20the%20talks%20cooled%20after%20the%20ICC%20issued%20a%20clarification%20on%20the%20matter.%20But%2C%20since%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20entire%20cricketing%20spectrum%20have%20been%20on%20the%20pitch%20for%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pitch%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20used%20in%20the%20final%2C%20has%20also%20been%20used%20in%20the%20India-Pakistan%20game%20in%20this%20World%20Cup%20before.%20It%20sported%20a%20darkish%20hue%2C%20a%20characteristic%20of%20a%20black%20soil%20surface.%20Such%20a%20surface%20would%20mean%20a%20lower%20bounce%20and%20some%20slow%20turn.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20teams%20chasing%20have%20won%20three%20of%20the%20four%20games%20at%20this%20ground%20in%20this%20World%20Cup.%20Dew%20will%20also%20be%20a%20factor%20here%2C%20unlike%20some%20other%20venues%20in%20this%20World%20Cup.%20The%20average%20first%20innings%20score%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20stadium%20in%20this%20World%20Cup%20is%20251.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAhmedabad%20Weather%20Report%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ERain%20hasn't%20had%20much%20say%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20with%20the%20second%20semi-final%20between%20Australia%20and%20South%20Africa%20being%20the%20only%20one%20to%20have%20had%20some%20sort%20of%20impact.%20As%20India%20take%20on%20the%20Aussies%20in%20the%20final%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20the%20skies%20are%20expected%20to%20remain%20clear.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ac