p%3EHaving%20suffered%20from%20cramps%20in%20extreme%20Mumbai%20heat%20in%20the%20semi-final%2C%20team's%20premier%20batter%20Virat%20Kohli%20skipped%20the%20optional%20net%20session%20for%20the%20second%20day%20in%20a%20row%20in%20order%20to%20remain%20fresh%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%20final%20against%20Australia%20on%20Sunday.%20En%20route%20his%2050th%20ODI%20hundred%2C%20Kohli%20had%20battled%20cramps%20but%20later%20fielded%20for%20the%20better%20part%20of%20the%20semi-final%20against%20New%20Zealand.%20With%20the%20Indian%20team%20having%20a%20hectic%20travel%20schedule%2C%20the%20support%20staff%20has%20nicely%20managed%20the%20workload%20of%20the%20players%20and%20hence%20Kohli%2C%20along%20with%20all%20the%20first%20eleven%20pacers%2C%20were%20given%20rest%20on%20the%20day.%20None%20of%20the%20three%20pacers%20or%20Kohli%20took%20part%20in%20the%20two%20pre-final%20sessions%20at%20Motera.%20Skipper%20Rohit%2C%20for%20the%20second%20day%20in%20a%20row%2C%20had%20a%20long%20and%20hard%20look%20at%20the%20strip%20and%20felt%20that%20there%20was%20a%20slight%20difference%20from%20the%20track%20on%20which%20they%20played%20against%20Pakistan%20on%20October%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20wicket%20(Pakistan%20game)%2C%20there%20was%20no%20grass%20on%20it.%20This%20wicket%20has%20some%20grass%20on%20it.%20That%20wicket%20looked%20a%20lot%20more%20drier%20than%20this%20one%20-%20I%20don't%20know%2C%20maybe%20you%20know%2C%20I%20still%20haven't%20looked%20today%20how%20the%20wicket%20is%20but%20from%20my%20understanding%20obviously%20it's%20slightly%20going%20to%20be%20on%20the%20slower%20side.%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20skipper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20not%20going%20to%20change%20too%20much%2C%20but%20it's%20always%20nice%20to%20see%20the%20pitch%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20game%20and%20then%20assess%20what%20you%20want%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20there%20is%20an%20option%20of%20playing%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20but%20it%20looks%20highly%20unlikely%20they%20will%20tinker%20with%20winning%20combination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20is%20something%20we've%20maintained%20for%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time%20and%20something%20that%20we've%20done%20before%20as%20well.%20So%2C%20it's%20not%20something%20new%20for%20us%20to%20come%20and%20assess%20the%20pitch%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20game%20and%20the%20players%20are%20aware%20of%20it%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20the%20skipper%20isn't%20sure%20how%20big%20a%20factor%20dew%20will%20be%20since%20the%20temperatures%20have%20dropped%20this%20time%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20terms%20of%20the%20conditions%20changing%2C%20yes%2C%20the%20temperature%20has%20dropped%20a%20little%20bit.%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20much%20of%20a%20dew%20factor%20there%20will%20be%20because%20against%20Pakistan%20in%20that%20game%2C%20when%20we%20trained%20before%20the%20game%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20dew%20but%20there%20was%20no%20dew%20during%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20even%20a%20few%20days%20back%20at%20Wankhede%2C%20we%20were%20training%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20dew%20on%20the%20game%20day%20there%20wasn't%20much%2C%20so%20that's%20why%20I%20keep%20saying%20the%20toss%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20a%20factor%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700359020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F8ph03ppo_c_625x300_18_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fwill-toss-play-a-big-role-in-cricket-world-cup-2023-final-rohit-sharma-gives-his-honest-verdict-4585821%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rohit%20Sharma%20gave%20his%20honest%20verdict%20on%20how%20much%20the%20toss%20can%20impact%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20final%20between%20India%20and%20Australia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A79%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv