%20changed%20policies%20before%20suspending%20pro-Palestine%20student%20groups.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20senior%20university%20executive%20confirmed%20the%20covert%20policy%20changes%20to%20the%20University%20Senate.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20is%20a%20growing%20point%20of%20conflict%20on%20United%20States%20college%20campuses.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EColumbia%20University%20Administrators%20covertly%20changed%20events%20policies%20before%20suspending%20two%20pro-Palestine%20student%20groups%2C%20according%20to%20the%20university%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGerald%20M.%20Rosberg%2C%20senior%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20university%2C%20informed%20the%20University%20Senate%20on%20Friday%20that%20university%20administrators%20had%20revised%20the%20policies%20without%20the%20knowledge%20of%20the%20senate%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.columbiaspectator.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F11%2F17%2Ftop-administration-revised-policies-cited-in-sjp-and-jvps-suspension-without-university-senate-input-rosberg-confirms%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EColumbia%20Spectator%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20I%20am%20going%20to%20be%20living%20with%20this%20for%20a%20long%20time%20to%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosberg%20said%20at%20the%20meeting%20according%20to%20the%20student%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20has%20become%20a%20controversial%20topic%20on%20college%20campuses%20throughout%20the%20U.S.%20since%20Hamas'%20October%207%20attack%20inside%20Israel%2C%20which%20killed%201%2C200%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20responded%20with%20air%20attacks%20and%20a%20ground%20invasion%20in%20Gaza%20that%20have%20so%20far%20killed%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20Palestinians%2C%20thousands%20of%20whom%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20children%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Hamas-led%20Palestinian%20Health%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20growing%20pro-Palestinian%20activist%20movement%20at%20American%20schools%20and%20colleges%20has%20stoked%20controversy%20and%20has%20been%20covered%20extensively%20in%20the%20media.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20California%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-grade-teacher-suspended-lesson-genocide-palestine-israel-hamas-war-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20grade%20teacher%20was%20suspended%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20giving%20students%20a%20lesson%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bgenocide%20in%20Palestine.%26quot%3B%20At%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%2C%20the%20decision%20to%20host%20a%20Palestine%20Writes%20Literary%20Festival%20caused%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversity-of-pennsylvania-major-donors-pulling-funding-israel-hamas-war-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseveral%20mega-donors%20to%20threaten%20their%20support%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Spectator%2C%20Columbia%20changed%20its%20events%20policy%20after%20student%20chapters%20of%20Students%20for%20Justice%20in%20Palestine%20and%20Jewish%20Voice%20for%20Peace%20protested%20on%20October%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColumbia%20ultimately%20suspended%20the%20university%20chapters%20of%20SJP%20and%20JVP%20on%20November%2010%20after%20the%20groups%20organized%20a%20walkout%2C%20which%20it%20says%20were%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeanine%20D'Armiento%2C%20University%20Senate%20executive%20committee%20chair%2C%20said%20the%20policy%20change%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Binconsistency%20in%20the%20events%20and%20the%20rules%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20she%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20going%20to%20accept%20any%20explanation%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20communication%20of%20the%20policy%20change%20was%20made%20clear%2C%26quot%3B%20Spectator%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Lurie%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Columbia%20chapter%20of%20the%20American%20Association%20of%20University%20Professors%2C%20said%20that%20administrators%20updating%20student%20group%20policies%20on%20their%20own%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bgross%20violation%26quot%3B%20of%20shared%20governance%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insidehighered.com%2Fnews%2Fstudents%2Ffree-speech%2F2023%2F11%2F17%2Fcolumbia-altered-policy-suspending-pro-palestinian-groups%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInside%20Higher%20Ed%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20they've%20done%20is%20taken%20something%20that%20should%20be%20running%20through%20existing%20disciplinary%20channels%20that%20involve%20our%20right%20of%20appeal%2C%20that%20involve%20advisory%20boards%2C%20that%20include%20faculty%20and%20student%20representation%2C%20and%20eliminated%20all%20of%20those%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColumbia%20did%20not%20immediately%20return%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%20Saturday%2C%20but%20a%20university%20spokesperson%20told%20Inside%20Higher%20Ed%20that%20the%20university%20sent%20the%20student%20groups%20%26quot%3Brestatements%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20policy%20updates%20before%20the%20walkout%20that%20led%20to%20their%20suspension.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%5BThe%20groups'%5D%20compliance%20with%20%5Bthe%20procedures%5D%20started%20to%20slip%2C%20and%20the%20%5Bgroups'%5D%20advisers%20issued%20numerous%20warnings%20that%20clearly%20laid%20out%20that%20failure%20to%20respect%20the%20required%20processes%20would%20have%20consequences%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freport-columbia-university-changed-policies-before-pro-palestine-group-suspensions-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700346346000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65590fdf4ca513d8242beda3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freport-columbia-university-changed-policies-b