C%20they%20mentioned%20to%20him%20that%20I%20was%20interested%20in%20getting%20into%20the%20trades.%20The%20carpenter%20connected%20me%20to%20an%20electrician%20who%20was%20hiring%2C%20and%20he%20gave%20me%20the%20rundown%20of%20doing%20an%20apprenticeship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20I%20started%20working%20at%20his%20company%2C%20BT%20Morin%20Electric.%20I%20work%20more%20than%2040%20hours%20a%20week%20and%20then%20do%20my%20online%20education%20at%20Vermont%20Technical%20College.%20On%20Mondays%20and%20Wednesdays%2C%20I%20have%20class%20from%205%3A30%20pm%20to%208%3A00%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20more%20than%2040%20other%20people%20in%20my%20class%20%E2%80%94%20of%20all%20ages.%20Most%20are%20men%2C%20but%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20the%20number%20of%20women%20who%20are%20enrolled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20four-year%20program.%20It%20only%20costs%20about%20%241%2C000%20a%20year%2C%20which%20I'm%20paying.%20My%20boss%20at%20BT%20Morin%20Electric%20offered%20to%20pay%20for%20my%20education%2C%20but%20then%20I%20would%20owe%20him%20a%20couple%20years%20of%20working%20after%20I%20get%20my%20license.%20I'd%20like%20to%20move%20away%20from%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%20in%20school%20we're%20learning%20about%20safety%2C%20electrical%20codes%2C%20and%20residential%20wiring.%20But%20I'm%20learning%20the%20most%20by%20working.%20I%20feel%20like%20in%20just%20two%20months%20I've%20learned%20more%20than%20my%20entire%20time%20in%20high%20school.%20We're%20hooking%20up%20generators%2C%20and%20running%20wiring%20throughout%20homes%20to%20outlets%2C%20lights%2C%20and%20appliances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20it's%20like%20solving%20a%20puzzle.%20Just%20today%2C%20there%20wasn't%20power%20in%20one%20room%20of%20this%20house%20we%20were%20working%20in.%20So%20we%20had%20to%20find%20the%20source%20of%20the%20problem%20by%20testing%20wires%20and%20tracing%20the%20flow%20of%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20challenging%20part%20is%20dealing%20with%20the%20guys%20I%20work%20with.%20We're%20a%20four-man%20crew.%20They%20like%20to%20mess%20with%20me%20because%20I'm%20the%20new%20guy.%20But%20I'm%20glad%20I%20get%20to%20wake%20up%20and%20go%20learn.%20It's%20just%20like%20school%2C%20except%20I'm%20getting%20paid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20earn%20%2415.50%20an%20hour%20now.%20That%20should%20increase%20when%20I%20demonstrate%20that%20I%20can%20do%20the%20work%20on%20my%20own.%20Once%20I%20get%20my%20license%20in%20a%20few%20years%2C%20I'm%20thinking%20about%20moving%20somewhere%20and%20potentially%20working%20at%20a%20bigger%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20like%20to%20get%20into%20the%20solar%20industry.%20I've%20done%20some%20research%20and%20it's%20like%2C%20why%20aren't%20we%20adding%20more%20solar%20than%20we%20are%20now%3F%20If%20I%20can%20use%20my%20skills%20to%20create%20a%20better%20world%2C%20I%20absolutely%20want%20to%20do%20that.%20I%20would%20feel%20good%20going%20to%20work%20knowing%20I'm%20helping%20solve%20a%20problem%20the%20Earth%20is%20facing.%20It'd%20be%20cool%20to%20come%20home%20and%20be%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20I%20created%20renewable%20energy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenz-skip-four-year-college-become-electrician-no-student-loans-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700328354000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654e528db788914e5553ed42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenz-skip-four-year-college-become-electrician-no-student-loans-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Grant%20Holderman%20knew%20college%20wasn't%20for%20him%20and%20is%20to%20be%20an%20electrician.%20%26quot%3BIt'd%20be%20cool%20to%20come%20home%20and%20be%20like%2C%20'Yeah%2C%20I%20created%20renewable%20energy.'%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cboudreau%40insider.com%20(Catherine%20Boudreau)%22%2C%22engagement%