g%20and%20maintaining%20charging%20stations%2C%20transmission%20lines%2C%20and%20electric%20appliances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20seeing%20this%20revolution%20to%20get%20off%20gas%20and%20fossil%20fuels%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Grant%20Shmelzer%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20Independent%20Electrical%20Contractors%20of%20Chesapeake%2C%20which%20runs%20an%20apprenticeship%20program%20in%20the%20Maryland-Virginia%20area.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20look%20at%20what%20the%20state%20and%20federal%20government%20is%20shooting%20for%2C%20it's%20all%20electric%20driven.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act%20is%20set%20to%20pour%20nearly%20%24400%20billion%20over%20the%20next%20decade%20into%20climate%20action%2C%20including%20tax%20breaks%20for%20solar%20and%20wind%20projects%2C%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20electric%20appliances%20like%20heat%20pumps%2C%20and%20low-carbon%20manufacturing.%20There%20are%20new%20loans%20and%20grants%20for%20transmission%20lines.%20Two%20dozen%20states%20have%20set%20their%20own%20goals%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.c2es.org%2Fcontent%2Fstate-climate-policy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eslash%20greenhouse-gas%20emissions%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20energy%2C%20transportation%2C%20and%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20data%20indicates%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bls.gov%2Fooh%2Fconstruction-and-extraction%2Felectricians.htm%23%3A~%3Atext%3Din%2520May%25202022.-%2CJob%2520Outlook%2Con%2520average%252C%2520over%2520the%2520decade.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eelectrician%20jobs%20are%20growing%20faster%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20the%20average%20of%20all%20occupations%2C%20with%2073%2C500%20openings%20expected%20each%20year%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%20That's%20more%20than%20triple%20the%20projected%20number%20of%20yearly%20openings%20for%20physicians%20and%20surgeons.%20Some%20industry%20estimates%20suggest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fqmerit.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhite-Paper-Electrification2030-Qmerit.pdf%3F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edemand%20for%20electricians%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20be%20even%20higher%20now%20that%20incentives%20from%20the%20IRA%20are%20ramping%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsletter.businessinsider.com%2Fclick%2F32857048.1808%2FaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxzLmdvdi9vZXMvY3VycmVudC9vZXM0NzIxMTEuaHRtP3V0bV9tZWRpdW09bmV3c2xldHRlciZlbWFpbD1jYm91ZHJlYXUlNDBpbnNpZGVyLmNvbSZ4PTgxMjhlMjllMzA3ZDhjMjYyMjg3MGM0M2QyZTgzMWEyMmNlNTAwOTI1NWExNTBkNTQ3MTcwMzVlOGNiMGQwYTYjc3Q%2F628bdf90094963f5ad0eef3eBb92ed97b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emean%20annual%20wage%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20electricians%20in%202022%20was%20about%20%2465%2C000%2C%20but%20salaries%20vary%20by%20state.%20In%20California%2C%20a%20master%20electrician%20can%20make%20as%20much%20as%20an%20attorney%20%E2%80%94%20or%20more%20than%20%24100%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20without%20racking%20up%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20student%20loan%20debt%2C%20said%20Tom%20Bowen%2C%20the%20president%20of%20Qmerit%2C%20a%20company%20in%20Irvine%20that%20connects%20homeowners%20and%20commercial%20properties%20with%20contractors%20who%20can%20install%20EV%20chargers%2C%20rooftop%20solar%20panels%2C%20and%20battery%20storage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20about%203%2C500%20contractors%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Canada%20and%20is%20adding%20new%20contractors%20to%20its%20platform%20every%20day%2C%20Bowen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20there%20aren't%20enough%20trained%20electricians%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20demand%2C%20partly%20because%20they're%20retiring%20at%20a%20faster%20rate%20than%20they're%20entering%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20experts%20said%20that%20reversing%20the%20trend%20would%20require%20overcoming%20several%20cultural%20hurdles%20and%20investing%20in%20apprenticeship%20programs.%20Traditionally%20the%20trades%20have