indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fhungary-needs-to-change-the-eu-not-leave-it-pm-viktor-orban%2Farticleshow%2F105318716.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20IDFA%20Award%20Acceptance%20Speech%2C%20Anand%20Patwardhan%20Calls%20For%20%E2%80%98Immediate%20Ceasefire%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Just%20Peace%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F25093726%2Fanand-patwardhan.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cspan%3EIndian%20documentary%20filmmaker%20Anand%20Patwardhan%20has%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20in%20his%20acceptance%20speech%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2023%2F11%2Fidfa-2023-documentary-awards-winners-1235615852%2F%5C%22%3EBest%20Editing%20award%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20International%20Documentary%20Festival%20Amsterdam%20(IDFA).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPatwardhan%20won%20the%20award%20for%20his%20film%20titled%20%3Cem%3EVasudhaiva%20Kutumbakam%2FThe%20World%20is%20Family%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20festival%2C%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20documentary%20gathering%2C%20has%20long%20been%20seen%20as%20being%20politically%20vocal%20and%20has%20come%20under%20criticism%20in%20its%20latest%20edition%20for%20attempting%20to%20tread%20carefully%20in%20the%20ongoing%20conflict.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20faced%20criticism%20first%20from%20some%20Israeli%20and%20American%20filmmakers%2C%20and%20then%20from%20Palestinian%20filmmakers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EDeadline%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20opening%20night%20ceremony%20of%20the%20festival%20last%20Wednesday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2023%2F11%2Finternational-documentary-festival-amsterdam-israel-gaza-