armony%20and%20with%20equal%20rights%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20should%20be%20emphasised.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPatwardhan%20also%20lauded%20those%20who%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20festival%2C%20those%20who%20stayed%20back%20to%20continue%20to%20debate%20and%20those%20who%20%E2%80%9Callowed%20the%20space%E2%80%9D%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20protests%20have%20been%20non-violent.%20Non-violence%20can%20build%20a%20global%20community.%20In%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20Palestinians%20and%20Jews%20are%20marching%20together%20with%20others%20to%20demand%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20and%20a%20just%20peace%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20acceptance%20speech%20is%20reproduced%20below%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EVasudhaiva%20Kutumbakam%2FThe%20World%20is%20Family%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAcceptance%20speech%20for%20Best%20Editing%20Award%20at%20IDFA%2C%202023%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20take%20this%20opportunity%20to%20amplify%20all%20international%20voices%20calling%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20in%20Palestine%2C%20Ukraine%20and%20other%20ongoing%20war%20zones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20river%20to%20the%20sea%2C%20Palestine%20will%20be%20free%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20misunderstood%20slogan.%20Some%20interpret%20it%20as%20a%20slogan%20calling%20for%20a%20One%20State%20solution%20and%20the%20ethnic%20cleansing%20of%20Jews.%20This%20misunderstanding%20is%20why%20the%20real%20meaning%20of%20the%20slogan%20should%20be%20explained%20and%20emphasized%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20a%20call%20for%20a%20land%20where%20Muslims%2C%20Jews%2C%20Christians%20and%20all%20others%20can%20live%20together%20in%20peace%20and%20harmony%20and%20with%20equal%20rights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20applaud%20those%20who%20pulled%20