0contradictions%20implicit%20in%20trying%20to%20create%20a%20new%20nation-state%20on%20land%20inhabited%20for%20many%20centuries%20by%20other%20nationals.%20He%20provided%20a%20bird%E2%80%99s-eye%20view%20of%20what%20Israel%20needed%20to%20do%20to%20be%20at%20peace%20with%20the%20Palestinians%20and%20explained%20how%20the%20Israeli%20state%2C%20barring%20brief%20interludes%20of%20political%20and%20intellectual%20sanity%2C%20had%20always%20militated%20against%20that%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20admitted%20that%20he%20found%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20October%207%20attack%20on%20Israeli%20civilians%20positively%20distasteful%2C%20even%20abhorrent%2C%20but%20reminded%20Morgan%20that%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20militancy%20had%20grown%20out%20of%20a%20reaction%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20systematic%20and%20brutal%20repression%20of%20the%20Palestinians.%20Piers%20Morgan%2C%20however%2C%20kept%20coming%20back%20to%20the%20same%20question%3A%20did%20Youssef%20concede%20that%2C%20after%207%20October%2C%20Israel%20was%20wholly%20justified%20in%20doing%20what%20it%20was%20now%20doing%2C%20namely%2C%20mounting%20on%20Gaza%20an%20all-out%20war%20the%20human%20costs%20of%20which%20were%20perhaps%20%E2%80%93unfortunately%20%E2%80%93%20quite%20heavy%2C%20but%20yet%20%3Cem%3Eunavoidable%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%C2%A0%20Youssef%2C%20it%20seemed%20to%20me%2C%20was%20incredulous%20that%20Morgan%20could%20persist%20in%20hoping%20that%20he%20would%20agree%20with%20what%20Morgan%20believed%20was%20a%20%3Cem%3Emoral%20%3C%2Fem%3Eimperative%2C%20as%20though%20the%20Hamas%20offensive%20had%20no%20context%20to%20it%2C%20no%20link%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20conversation%20eventually%20ended%20in%20an%20essentially%20fatuous%20exchange%20of%20pleasantries%2C%20with%20precious%20little%20achieved%20by%20way%20of%20a%20shared%20understanding%20of%20the%20contours%20of%20a%20great%20tragedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20me%20clarify%20that%20Piers%20Morgan%20is%20no%20%3Cem%3Efaux%20