spective%20examination%20of%20its%20diverse%20forms%20and%20contents%20to%20be%20able%20to%20resonate%20and%20develop%20its%20transformative%20capacity.%20Categorical%2C%20one-sided%20reductions%20and%20over-simplifications%20of%20complex%20contexts%20threaten%20to%20nip%20any%20such%20examination%20in%20the%20bud%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20wrote%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHoskote%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fcurator-ranjit-hoskote-resigns-from-documentas-finding-committee-over-anti-semitism-allegations%5C%22%3Eresignation%3C%2Fa%3E%20followed%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sueddeutsche.de%2Fkultur%2Franjit-hoskote-documenta-antisemitismus-bds-1.6301063%3Freduced%3Dtrue%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20daily%20%3Cem%3ES%C3%BCddeutsche%20Zeitung%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20November%209%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaying%20that%20a%202019%20letter%20signed%20by%20Hoskote%2C%20among%20others%2C%20was%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fdocumenta-committee-resigns-in-wake-of-antisemitism-claims%2Fa-67406086%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclearly%20antisemitic%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20culture%20minister%20Claudia%20Roth%20threatened%20to%20withdraw%20public%20funding%20for%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202019%20letter%20was%20published%20as%20part%20of%20the%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3ESuddeutsche%20Zeitung%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0on%20November%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%2C%20circulated%20by%20the%20Boycott%2C%20Divestment%2C%20and%20Sanctions%20(BDS)%20global%20movement%2C%20aimed%20to%20exert%20pressure%20on%20Tel%20Aviv%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20occupied%20Palestinian%20territories%20and%20adhere%20to%20human%20rights%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEttinger%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20on%20November%2012%20was%20unrelated%20to%20the%20controversy%20surrounding%20Hoskote.%20%3Cem%3EARTnews%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20her%20decision%20was%20prompted%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdark%20times%E2%80%9D%20affecting%20her%20country%2C%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20letter%2C%20the%20four%20members%20said%20that%20they%20understand%20that%20in%20view%20of%20its%20past%2C%20Germany%20has%20%E2%80%9Cdistinct%20social%20and%20political%20responsibilities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20great%20sensitivity%20towards%20all%20anti-Semitic%20tendencies%20bears%20eloquent%20witness%20to%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20the%20nation%20has%20internalised%20this%20responsibility.%20The%20ongoing%20fulfilment%20of%20this%20very%20responsibility%20deserves%20the%20greatest%20appreciation%2C%20especially%20now%2C%20when%20alarming%20signs%20of%20deep-rooted%20anti-Semitism%20are%20once%20again%20making%20themselves%20felt%20around%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20however%2C%20this%20awareness%20of%20special%20responsibilities%20runs%20the%20risk%20of%20being%20misused%20for%20opinion%20politics%20in%20order%20to%20suppress%20undesirable%20approaches%20and%20their%20broad%20and%20open%20discussion%20right%20from%20the%20start.%20Instead%20of%20debate%20and%20discussion%2C%20over-simplification%20and%20prejudgments%20are%20thus%20all%20too%20easily%20substituted%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20edition%20as%20well%2C%20the%20exhibition%20was%20engulfed%20in%20a%20scandal%20around%20its%20alleged%20proximity%20to%20BDS%20and%20a%20dispute%20over%20anti-Semitic%20iconography.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20members%20said%20in%20the%20letter%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20this%20emotional%20and%20intellectual%20climate%20of%20over-simplification%20of%20complex%20realities%20and%20its%20resulting%20restrictive%20limitations%2C%20which%20has%20been%20prevalent%20since%20documenta15%20and%20especially%20against%20the%20background%20of%20the%20current%20crises%20our%20world%20is%20facing%2C%20that%20makes%20it%20impossible%20for%20us%20to%20conceive%20of%20a%20strong%20and%20signal%20exhibition%20project%2C%20and%20consequently%20to%20allow%20for%20a%20responsible%20continuation%20of%20the%20selection%20process%20to%20determine%20a%20curatorial%20concept%20for%20documenta16.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Finding%20Committee%2C%20according%20to%20the%20organisers%2C%20%E2%80%9Chas%20the%20task%20of%20inviting%20pioneering%20figures%20in%20contemporary%20art%20to%20apply%20to%20take%20on%20the%20role%20of%20Artistic%20Direction%20of%20documenta%2016%2C%20and%20to%20select%20the%20most%20promising%20format%20from%20the%20concepts%20presented.%20Appointment%20of%20the%20Artistic%20Direction%20is%20targeted%20for%20late%202023%20%2F%20early%202024.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20four%20members%20said%20that%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20current%20developments%2C%20there%20is%20no%20space%20for%20%E2%80%9Copen%20exchange%20of%20ideas%E2%80%9D%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20current%20circumstances%20we%20do%20not%20believe%20that%20there%20is%20a%20space%20in%20Germany%20for%20an%20open%20exchange%20of%20ideas%20and%20the%20development%20of%20complex%20and%20nuanced%20artistic%20approaches%20that%20documenta%20artists%20and%20curators%20deserve.%20We%20do%20not%20believe%20that%20any%20acceptable%20conditions%20can%20be%20created%20in%20short%20term%20and%20consider%20it%20to%20be%20disrespectful%20of%20documenta%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20to%20simply%20remain%20content%20with%20the%20current%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20four%20members%E2%80%99%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20Hoskote%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20on%20November%2012%2C%20Ettinger%20had%20also%20stepped%20down%C2%A0%20for%20reasons%20that%20she%20stated%20were%20not%20connected%20to%20the%20accusations%20levelled%20against%20Hoskote%20but%20because%20Israel%20was%20enduring%20%E2%80%9Cdark%20times.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700301880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F18153253%2Fimage-1520.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fno-space-in-germany-for-open-exchange-of-ideas-after-hoskote-other-documenta-panel-members-quit%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mumbai-based%20author%20and%20curator%20Ranjit%20Hoskote%20resigned%20from%20the%20Finding%20Committee%C2%A0for%20the%20upcoming%2016th%20edition%20of%20Documenta%20in%20Kassel%2C%20Germany%20last%20week%20amid%20accusations%20of%20'anti-Semitism'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fno-space-in-germany-for-open-exchange-of-ideas-after-hoskote-other-documenta-panel-members-quit%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20navy%20used%20sonar%20pulses%20against%20divers%2C%20Australia%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700301316000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1311A%2Fproduction%2F_131760187_mediaitem131760186.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2F67461081%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Canberra%20says%20naval%20divers%20suffered%20injuries%20following%20a%20high-seas%20encounter%20with%20a%20Chinese%20warship.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A840%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2F67461081%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2F67461081.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2F67461081.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Nearly%202%20Years%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20HC%20Grants%20Bail%20to%20Kashmiri%20Journalist%20Fahad%20Shah%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F12194450%2Fimage-44.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENearly%20two%20years%20after%20his%20arrest%2C%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20high%20court%20has%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20the%20release%20of%20Kashmiri%20journalist%20Fahad%20Shah%20by%20granting%20him%20bail%20on%20Friday%2C%20November%2017%2C%20in%20a%20case%20involving%20the%20publication%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cseditious%E2%80%9D%20article%20in%20his%20digital%20magazine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fkashmir-scholar-arrested-2011-article-fahad-shah-fresh-charges%5C%22%3Ewas%20held%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20charges%20of%20terrorism%20for%20publishing%20the%20article%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EThe%20shackles%20of%20slavery%20will%20break%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20his%20now-defunct%20magazine%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%202011.%20The%20opinion%20piece%20was%20authored%20by%20Aala%20Fazili%2C%20a%20University%20of%20Kashmir%20scholar%20who%20has%20also%20been%20arrested%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20and%20senior%20advocate%20P.N.%20Raina%20said%20that%20the%20court%20quashed%20the%20charges%20under%20Sections%2018%20(terror%20conspiracy)%20and%20121%20(waging%20war%20against%20the%20country)%20of%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20and%20153-B%20(imputations%2C%20assertions%20prejudicial%20to%20national-integration)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20against%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20(Shah)%20will%20face%20trial%20under%20Section%2013%20(abetting%20unlawful%20activities)%20of%20the%20UAPA%20and%20Sections%2035%20(receiving%20foreign%20funds%20illegally)%20and%2039%20(offences%20by%20companies)%20under%20the%20Foreign%20Contribution%20(Regulation)%20Act%2C%202010%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raina%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20filed%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20State%20Investigation%20Agency%20at%20the%20CIJ%20police%20station%20in%20Jammu%20on%20April%204%2C%202022%20(FIR%20No%3A%2001%2F2022)%2C%20around%2011%20years%20after%20Fazili%E2%80%99s%20piece%20appeared%20in%20the%20magazine.%20A%20chargesheet%20was%20filed%20in%20the%20case%20last%20year%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%20this%20year%2C%20the%20high%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffahad-shah-public-safety-act-jammu-kashmir-high-court%5C%22%3Ehad%20quashed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Public%20Safety%20Act%20(PSA)%20invoked%20against%20Shah%20by%20terming%20the%20allegations%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20as%20%E2%80%9Cmere%20surmise%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cvague%20and%20bald%20assertions%E2%80%9D.%20It%20also%20accused%20the%20authorities%20of%20snatching%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cconstitutional%20and%20legal%20rights%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amnestyusa.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2Fasa200012011en_11.pdf%5C%22%3EAmnesty%20International%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20PSA%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Clawless%20law%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20has%20been%20used%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Crevolving%20door%E2%80%9D%20policy%20for%20suspects%20against%20whom%20the%20government%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20has%20little%20or%20no%20evidence%20to%20bring%20formal%20charges%20against%20them%20in%20the%20court%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%E2%80%99s%20PSA%20dossier%2C%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20alleged%20that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Cfilled%20with%20hatred%20against%20%5Bthe%5D%20Union%20of%20India%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Cpromoted%20separatism%E2%80%9D.%20It%20further%20alleged%20that%20his%20%E2%80%9Cactivities%20seem%20to%20be%20prejudicial%20to%20the%20sovereignty%2C%20security%2C%20integrity%2C%20peace%20and%20tranquility%20of%20the%20UT%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20also%20the%20Union%20of%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dossier%20also%20accused%20Shah%20of%20arranging%20%E2%80%9Clogistical%20support%20for%20anti-national%20activities%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cinciting%20violence%20thereby%20leading%20to%20disturbance%20in%20public%20order%E2%80%9D%20while%20terming%20him%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cthreat%20to%20public%20order.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20court%20quashed%20the%20PSA%20proceedings%20against%20him%2C%20Shah%20was%20arrested%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20State%20Investigation%20Agency%20in%20the%20case%20in%20which%20he%20has%20now%20been%20granted%20bail.%20He%20has%20been%20granted%20bail%20in%20three%20other%20criminal%20cases%20brought%20against%20him%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20for%20the%20reporting%20done%20by%20his%20magazine%20on%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20was%20charged%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20May%202020%20over%20the%20coverage%20of%20a%20gun%20battle%20between%20militants%20and%20security%20forces%20in%20Srinagar.%20In%20the%20encounter%E2%80%99s%20aftermath%2C%20local%20residents%20had%20alleged%20that%20security%20forces%20took%20away%20their%20precious%20belongings%2C%20a%20charge%20denied%20by%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20and%20the%20denial%20were%20widely%20reported%20by%20local%20and%20national%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20on%20January%2030%2C%202021%2C%20Shah%20was%20booked%20under%20Sections%20153%20(provocation%20with%20intent%20to%20cause%20riot)%20and%20505%20(statements%20conducive%20to%20public%20mischief)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20for%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20alleged%20that%20the%20Army%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpressuring%E2%80%9D%20the%20management%20of%20a%20private%20school%20in%20Shopian%20to%20organise%20the%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20had%20denied%20the%20charge%20and%20proceeded%20to%20file%20a%20criminal%20case%20against%20Shah%2C%20who%20was%20later%20granted%20bail%20by%20a%20court.%20Shah%20has%20reportedly%20faced%20six%20cases%20of%20intimidation%20between%20June%202017%20and%20January%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20case%20pertains%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20coverage%20of%20a%20gun%20battle%20in%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Pulwama%20district%20in%20which%20three%20militants%2C%20including%20a%20top%20commander%2C%20were%20gunned%20down%20last%20year.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20accused%20of%20%E2%80%9Cglorifying%20terrorist%20activities%E2%80%9D%20and%20causing%20%E2%80%9Cdisaffection%20against%20the%20country%E2%80%9D%20by%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cincorrect%20reporting%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2019%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20pulled%20down%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%20website%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Information%20and%20Technology%20Act%2C%202000%2C%20a%20controversial%20law%20which%20has%20been%20criticised%20by%20the%20free%20speech%20activists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPress%20freedom%20in%20India%20has%20suffered%20relentless%20blows%20in%20recent%20years%20under%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%20According%20to%20the%20World%20Press%20Freedom%20Index%E2%80%99s%20latest%20report%2C%20India%20slipped%20to%20161%20out%20of%20180%20countries%20this%20year%2C%20losing%2011%20more%20spots%20as%20compared%20to%20the%202022%20ranking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Paris-based%20press%20freedom%20watchdog%20Reporters%20Without%20Borders%2C%20India%20has%20been%20using%20%E2%80%9Ccharges%20of%20defamation%2C%20sedition%2C%20contempt%20of%20court%20and%20endangering%20national%20security%20%E2%80%A6%20increasingly%20..%20against%20journalists%20critical%20of%20the%20government%2C%20who%20are%20branded%20as%20%E2%80%98anti-national%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%20The%20government%20has%20denied%20these%20charges%2C%20accusing%20the%20watchdog%20of%20%E2%80%9Csubverting%20the%20democratic%20freedoms%20all%20over%20the%20world%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%2