as%20been%20stopped%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20National%20Highways%20and%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20Limited%20saidhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frescue-work-in-uttarakhand-tunnel-paused-after-loud-cracking-sound-4583724%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20pipes%20are%20being%20used%20to%20supply%20the%20workers%20with%20food%2C%20water%20and%20medicines.%20In%20addition%2C%20rescue%20workers%20have%20been%20able%20to%20dug%20through%2024%20metres%20of%20the%2060%20m%20debris%20to%20lay%20a%20pipe%2C%20which%20would%20help%20the%20trapped%20men%20crawl%20out%20of%20the%20tunnel%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67437754%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20work%20continues%20at%20this%20rate%2C%20it%20will%20take%20another%2040-48%20hours%20to%20rescue%20the%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Colonel%20Deepak%20Patil%2C%20who%20is%20overseeing%20the%20rescue%20operations%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Uttarakhand%3A%20Uttarkashi%20tunnel%20rescue%20%7C%20Morning%20visuals%20from%20the%20spot%3B%20relief%20and%20rescue%20work%20halted%20at%20Silkyara%20Tunnel%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20ANI%20Anshu%20Manish%20Khulko%2C%20Director%20of%20the%20tunnel-making%20company%20NHIDCL%2C%20said%20that%20at%20present%20the%20drilling%20work%20in%20the%20tunnel%20has%20stopped.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FZhNAsdAtRX%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FZhNAsdAtRX%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1725703970193392109%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2018%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20rescue%20operation%20resumed%20on%20Saturday%20morning%20(November%2018).%20However%2C%20the%20drilling%20work%20is%20currently%20halted%20as%20a%20new%20machine%20from%20Indore%20is%20expected%20to%20reach%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20workers%20have%20been%20reported%20to%20be%20safe%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdehradun%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-crash-collapse-news-live-updates-uttarkashi-silkyara-ndrf-sdrf-trapped-labourers-rescue-operation%2Fliveblog%2F105275038.cms%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20newspaper%20also%20reported%20that%20workers%20who%20are%20engaged%20in%20rescue%20work%20are%20fearing%20to%20enter%20the%20tunnel%20after%20they%20heard%20the%20loud%20cracking%20noise%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20workers%20have%20been%20trapped%20for%20the%20past%20six%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%2040%20workers%2C%20officials%20told%20%3Cem%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%2015%20are%20from%20Jharkhand%2C%20eight%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20five%20from%20Odisha%2C%20four%20from%20Bihar%2C%20three%20from%20Bengal%2C%20and%20two%20each%20from%20Assam%20and%20Uttarakhand%2C%20with%20one%20from%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20Char%20Dham%20all-weather%20accessibility%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700291253000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14115024%2FScreenshot-2023-11-14-at-11.50.16%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-rescue-40-workers-trapped-drilling-work-halted%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20rescue%20operation%20was%20suspended%20on%20Friday%2C%20November%2017%2C%20when%20a%20loud%20cracking%20sound%20was%20heard%20in%20the%20tunnel.%20This%2C%20per%20reports%2C%20happened%20during%20the%20positioning%20of%20a%20pipe.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-rescue-40-workers-trapped-drilling-work-halted%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Surveillance%20Is%20Your%20Friend%3A%20For%20Many%2C%20a%20CCTV%20Camera%20Is%20a%20Safety%20Net%20Against%20Police%20Excess%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17164343%2FUntitled-design-8-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20sleuths%20of%20the%20National%20Investigating%20Agency%20suddenly%20descended%20on%20human%20rights%20defender%20and%20school%20teacher%20Abdul%20Wahid%20Shaikh%E2%80%99s%20house%20on%20October%2011%2C%20he%20knew%20exactly%20what%20he%20needed%20to%20do%20next.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20had%20been%20monitoring%20the%20three%20CCTVs%20that%20are%20installed%20on%20the%20front%20and%20the%20rear%20of%20his%20house%20%E2%80%93%20a%20chawl%20in%20Vikhroli%2C%20a%20densely%20populated%20area%20in%20suburban%20Mumbai.%20The%20cameras%20told%20him%20that%20a%20group%20of%20men%20and%20women%20%E2%80%93%20some%20dressed%20in%20Mumbai%20police%E2%80%99s%20uniform%20and%20a%20few%20in%20civil%20clothes%20%E2%80%93%20had%20converged%20outside%20his%20house.%20Some%20of%20them%20were%20armed%20and%20few%20others%20with%20batons%20were%20aggressively%20banging%20at%20the%20door%20asking%20him%20to%20immediately%20let%20them%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20police%20had%20landed%20at%20his%20place%20at%205%20am.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20440px)%2085vw%2C%20440px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17165416%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-4.54.09%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17165416%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-4.54.09%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%20832w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17165416%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-4.54.09%25E2%2580%25AFPM-292x300.png%20292w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685240%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22453%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAbdul%20Wahid%20Shaikh%20at%20his%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20policemen%20discovered%20the%20CCTV%20cameras%20outside%20his%20house%2C%20they%20began%20hitting%20it%20with%20their%20batons%2C%20destroying%20one%20of%20them%20mounted%20right%20over%20the%20door.%20This%20action%20was%20captured%20by%20the%20adjacent%20CCTV%20camera.%20Shaikh%2C%20holed%20up%20in%20his%20house%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20two%20children%2C%20kept%20pleading%20with%20the%20police%20to%20stop%20destroying%20his%20property%20and%20simply%20show%20them%20an%20official%20notice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnlike%20the%2020%20other%20locations%20that%20the%20NIA%20team%20had%20reached%20the%20same%20day%2C%20to%20raid%20houses%20and%20also%20simultaneously%20arrest%20people%20in%20the%20ongoing%20probe%20against%20alleged%20Popular%20Front%20of%20India%20(PFI)%20members%2C%20and%20their%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20%E2%80%9Cunlawful%20and%20anti-national%20activities%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20raid%20at%20Shaikh%E2%80%99s%20received%20maximum%20traction%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20One%20reason%20is%20that%20Shaikh%2C%20who%20has%20already%20endured%20nine%20long%20years%20of%20incarceration%20(only%20to%20be%20later%20acquitted%20by%20the%20trial%20court)%2C%20is%20a%20well%20known%20prisoners%E2%80%99%20rights%20activist.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20reason%2C%20and%20more%20plausible%20in%20this%20case%2C%20is%20that%20Shaikh%20was%20able%20to%20immediately%20substantiate%20his%20fear%20and%20accusations%20of%20police%20excess%20with%20ample%20video%20evidence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECollection%20of%20evidence%2C%20and%20the%20need%20to%20satiate%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20requirement%20of%20%E2%80%9Cproving%20one%E2%80%99s%20innocence%E2%80%9D%20even%20when%20one%20is%20not%20implicated%20in%20any%20criminal%20case%2C%20however%2C%20has%20come%20at%20a%20huge%20cost%2C%20Shaikh%20says.%20The%20one%20that%20hurts%20him%20and%20his%20family%20the%20most%20is%20the%20absolute%20compromise%20of%20their%20personal%20space%20and%20privacy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVisits%20without%20reason%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20Control%20of%20Organised%20Crime%20Act%20(MCOCA)%20court%20in%202015%20acquitted%20him%20of%20all%20charges%20in%20the%20July%2011%2C%202006%20serial%20train%20blast%20case.%20Although%20his%20defence%20team%20was%20able%20to%20prove%20his%20innocence%20in%20the%20court%2C%20the%20police%20visits%20without%20any%20particular%20reason%2C%20summons%20to%20nearby%20police%20stations%20have%20continued%20over%20years.%20Shaikh%20knew%20if%20he%20had%20to%20ensure%20he%20does%20not%20end%20up%20in%20jail%20again%2C%20he%20had%20to%20put%20himself%20under%20constant%20watch.%20And%20not%20just%20him%2C%20but%20also%20his%20wife%20Sajida%20Tabassum%20and%20two%20children.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%20the%20two%20cameras%20outside%20his%20house%2C%20he%20was%20also%20compelled%20to%20install%20a%20camera%20in%20the%20living%20room%20of%20his%20modest%20flat.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20camera%20was%20installed%20to%20ensure%20that%20police%20follow%20the%20due%20process%20when%20they%20enter%20the%20house%20and%20do%20not%20harass%20my%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20His%20wife%2C%20who%20practices%20purdah%2C%20was%20opposed%20to%20this%20initially.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20complained%20of%20not%20feeling%20at%20ease%20inside%20her%20own%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDisturbing%20it%20may%20be%2C%20Shaikh%E2%80%99s%20is%20still%20not%20a%20one-of-a-kind%20case.%20Many%20individuals%2C%20predictably%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20who%20have%20faced%20police%20atrocity%20and%20the%20brutalities%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20carceral%20system%2C%20have%20taken%20refuge%20in%20putting%20themselves%20under%20CCTV%20surveillance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EState-imposed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20the%20discourse%20around%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%20in%20India%20is%20at%20a%20crucial%20point%2C%20here%20is%20a%20large%20community%20of%20people%20%E2%80%93%20facing%20both%20police%20excesses%20and%20fake%20criminal%20charges%20%E2%80%93%20forced%20to%20forsake%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20privacy.%20While%20the%20state%20might%20not%20be%20explicitly%20seen%20indulging%20in%20surveillance%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20it%20still%20is%20a%20state-imposed%20surveillance%2C%20says%2039-year-old%20Mohammad%20Bilal%20Gulam%20Rasul%20Kagazi%20from%20Surat%20district%20in%20Gujarat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKagazi%2C%20a%20lawyer%2C%20who%20focuses%20on%20cases%20of%20tribal%20rights%2C%20has%20long%20been%20a%20victim%20of%20police%20vendetta.%20As%20a%20part%20of%20his%20legal%20practice%2C%20Kagazi%20has%20been%20fighting%20cases%20for%20the%20Adivasi%20community%20of%20the%20region%2C%20raising%20issues%20of%20police%20atrocities%20and%20land%20encroachment%2C%20among%20others.%20And%20in%20the%20process%2C%20he%20says%2C%20the%20state%20began%20looking%20at%20him%20as%20an%20adverse%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Kagazi%20has%20had%20multiple%20cases%20filed%20against%20him%2C%20all%20directly%20relating%20to%20his%20lawyering%20and%20activism%20in%20the%20region.%20In%202019%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsurat-advocate-alleges-harassment-for-taking-up-cases-against-police-officials%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20published%20a%20detailed%20report%20on%20Kagazi%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20police%20harassment%20he%20had%20been%20facing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKagazi%2C%20too%2C%20has%20had%20to%20install%20cameras%20all%20around%20his%20house.%20These%20cameras%2C%20he%20says%2C%20visibly%20infringe%20on%20his%20privacy.%20But%20they%20also%20help%20provide%20him%20with%20some%20sense%20of%20security.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20police%20too%20are%20apprehensive%20of%20barging%20into%20my%20house%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Burden%20of%20innocence%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20unrest%20against%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20and%20two%20other%20imminent%20countrywide%20exercises%2C%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20and%20the%20National%20Population%20Register%20(NPR)%20grew%20in%202019%2C%20many%20Muslim%20families%20felt%20that%20they%20could%20no%20longer%20rely%20on%20the%20state%20for%20their%20security%20for%20it%20was%20the%20state%20machinery%20they%20feared%20the%20most.%20Incidents%20of%20houses%20being%20raided%20both%20by%20the%20police%20and%20local%20Hindu%20thugs%20were%20rampant%20during%20that%20period.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Khalapar%2C%20a%20Muslim-dominated%20locality%20of%20Muzaffarnagar%20district%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20almost%20every%20house%20decided%20to%20instal%20cameras%20in%20and%20around%20them.%20Khalapar%2C%20where%20relatively%20well%20off%20Muslim%20families%20reside%2C%20ended%20up%20spending%20on%20an%20average%20Rs%2030-40%2C000%20in%20getting%20the%20installations%20done.%20Today%2C%20activist%20Ravish%20Babu%20says%2C%20the%20entire%20region%20is%20under%20a%20%E2%80%9Cself-%20imposed%20surveillance%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBabu%20%E2%80%93%20a%20law%20student%20and%20a%20young%20activist%20from%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20who%20organised%20many%20anti-CAA%20protests%20in%20the%20district%20%E2%80%93%20too%20had%20to%20get%20multiple%20cameras%20installed%20around%20his%20two-storey%20house%20after%20the%20local%20police%20frequently%20visited%20his%20house%20and%20allegedly%20harassed%20both%20him%20and%20his%20family%20members.%20Along%20with%20deterring%20the%20police%2C%20Babu%20says%2C%20he%20is%20also%20able%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccollect%20evidence%E2%80%9D%20of%20his%20physical%20movement%20if%20that%20was%20to%20ever%20be%20necessary.%20%E2%80%9CUnder%20the%20current%20regime%2C%20the%20burden%20of%20proving%20one%E2%80%99s%20innocence%20is%20no%20more%20on%20the%20state%20but%20on%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20self%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20August%202017%2C%20in%20a%20historical%20ruling%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20held%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98right%20to%20privacy%E2%80%99%20is%20protected%20as%20an%20intrinsic%20part%20of%20the%20right%20to%20life%20and%20personal%20liberty%20under%20Article%2021%20and%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20fundamental%20freedoms%20guaranteed%20by%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20surrender%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrivacy%20is%20a%20constitutional%20core%20of%20human%20dignity.%20At%20its%20core%2C%20right%20to%20privacy%20should%20ensure%20preservation%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20personal%20space%2C%20along%20with%20the%20inviolability%20of%20marriage%2C%20procreation%2C%20the%20home%20and%20even%20sexual%20orientation.%20But%20by%20putting%20themselves%20under%20the%20constant%20watch%20of%20pervasive%20cameras%2C%20individuals%20are%20forced%20to%20surrender%20their%20privacy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20nothing%20fashionable%20about%20installing%20so%20many%20cameras%20in%20and%20outside%20one%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20says%20a%20young%20lawyer%20from%20rural%20Maharashtra.%20A%20Muslim%20man%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20a%20decade%20ago%20for%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20a%20terror%20module%2C%20he%20studied%20law%20after%20his%20release.%20He%20too%20had%20had%20cameras%20installed%20everywhere%20around%20him.%20But%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20completed%20law%20and%20began%20practicing%20in%20a%20local%20court%2C%20he%20got%20rid%20of%20the%20cameras.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20I%20can%20use%20my%20court%20appearance%20as%20evidence%20that%20I%20am%20not%20involved%20in%20any%20anti-national%20activities%2C%20that%20the%20police%20are%20ever%20willing%20to%20implicate%20me%20and%20many%20educated%20men%20like%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17165018%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-17-at-2.13.23-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17165018%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-17-at-2.13.23-PM.jpeg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17165018%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-17-at-2.13.23-PM-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685237%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EZainab%20(centre%2C%20in%20yellow).%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20matter%20how%20%E2%80%9Ccreepy%E2%80%9D%20it%20may%20be%2C%20cameras%20have%20for%20long%20provided%20a%20sense%20of%20security%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20says%20Zainab%20Siddiqui%2C%20a%20Lucknow-based%20activist.%20When%20her%20family%20was%20targeted%20in%202019%20for%20actively%20participating%20in%20the%20anti-CAA%20and%20anti-NRC%20protests%2C%20Zainab%20had%20filmed%20the%20police%20atrocity%20on%20her%20phone.%20Her%20father%20was%20arrested%20and%20her%20then%20minor%20brother%20was%20illegally%20detained%20by%20the%20police.%20Zainab%20had%20made%20the%20videos%20public%20soon%20after.%20They%20garnered%20huge%20support%20for%20her%20family%20from%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EZainab%20says%20she%20and%20her%20father%20have%20continued%20with%20their%20work.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20have%20also%20lived%20under%20the%20constant%20fear%20of%20getting%20targeted%20any%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20Zainab%E2%80%99s%20family%20too%20is%20weighing%20on%20the%20pros%20and%20cons%20of%20installing%20cameras%20in%20their%20family%20house%20in%20Lucknow.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20feels%20it%20is%20necessary.%20But%20we%20are%20wary%20of%20the%20many%20compromises%20that%20we%20will%20be%20making%20in%20the%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700289047000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17164343%2FUntitled-design-8-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwhen-surveillance-is-your-friend-for-many-a-cctv-camera-is-a-safety-net-against-police-excess%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'There%20is%20nothing%20fashionable%20about%20installing%20so%20many%20cameras%20in%20and%20outside%20one%E2%80%99s%20house%2C'%20says%20a%20Muslim%20lawyer.%20And%20yet%2C%20doing%20this%20has%20helped%20members%20of%20the%20community%20prove%20unfair%20police%20action%20against%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwhen-surveillance-is-your-friend-for-many-a-cctv-camera-is-a-safety-net-against-police-excess%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20India%E2%80%99s%20Summit%20for%20Global%20South%2C%20Leaders%20Raise%20Strong%20Concerns%20Over%20Ongoing%20Conflict%20in%20West%20Asia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F18114014%2Fimage-1518.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20was%20a%20common%20thread%20in%20the%20discussions%20at%20the%20second%20Voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20summit%2C%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20referring%20to%20%E2%80%9Cnew%20challenges%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20geopolitical%20crisis%20that%20have%20caused%20thousands%20of%20deaths%20over%20the%20last%20one%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%20(November%2017)%2C%20India%20held%20the%20second%20virtual%20Voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20summit.%20The%20first%20summit%20was%20held%20in%20January%20this%20year.%20It%20was%20part%20of%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20positioning%20as%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20developing%20world%20ahead%20of%20the%20G-20%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20opening%20session%20for%20leaders%2C%20Modi%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20are%20all%20seeing%20that%20new%20challenges%20are%20emerging%20from%20events%20in%20the%20West%20Asia%20region%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20reiterated%20that%20India%20had%20%E2%80%9Ccondemned%20the%20heinous%20terrorist%20attack%20in%20Israel%20on%20October%207%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Indian%20leader%20then%20noted%20that%20New%20Delhi%20has%20also%20called%20for%20restraint%20as%20well%20as%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20deaths%20of%20civilians%20in%20the%20conflict%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas.%20After%20talking%20to%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%2C%20we%20have%20also%20sent%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Palestine.%20It%20is%20time%20that%20the%20countries%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20speak%20with%20one%20voice%20for%20the%20greater%20global%20good%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2012%2C000%20civilians%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2Fliveblog%2F2023%2F10%2F28%2Fisrael-hamas-war-live-invasion-under-way-as-gaza-cut-off-from-the-world%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%20killed%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Gaza%20in%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20counter-strikes%2C%20following%20Hamas%20attack%20that%20left%20over%201%2C400%20Israelis%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20most%20of%20the%20global%20south%20had%20spoken%20rather%20unanimously%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%20when%20it%20passed%20a%20resolution%20on%20October%2027%2C%20calling%20for%20humanitarian%20pauses%20in%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%20operations%20against%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza.%20Among%20the%20global%20south%2C%20the%20only%20major%20outliers%20had%20been%20India%20and%20the%20Philippines%20who%20had%20abstained%2C%20while%20most%20of%20Asia%2C%20Africa%2C%20and%20Latin%20Africa%20voted%20yes%20on%20the%20resolution%20tabled%20by%20Jordan%20and%20the%20Arab%20League.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Indian%20foreign%20secretary%20Vinay%20Kwatra%20told%20reporters%20that%20all%20the%20leaders%20expressed%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%20concern%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20deteriorating%20situation%20in%20West%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20leaders%20spoke%2C%20almost%20all%20the%20leaders%2C%20spoke%20about%20the%20challenges%20of%20terrorism%2C%20the%20need%20to%20provide%20humanitarian%20assistance%2C%20horror%20at%20the%20civilian%20casualties%20due%20to%20the%20conflict.%20These%20three%20were%20the%20threads%20that%20were%20sort%20of%20common%20to%20all%20the%20interventions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20at%20a%20late%20night%20media%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20Indian%20diplomat%20also%20said%20that%20there%20had%20been%20discussion%20on%20the%20need%20to%20have%20access%20to%20sustainable%20credit%2C%20which%20did%20not%20add%20to%20the%20debt%20burden%20of%20most%20countries.%20When%20asked%20if%20the%20topic%20was%20an%20indictment%20of%20China%E2%80%99s%20policy%2C%20Kwatra%20said%20that%20no%20names%20were%20taken%2C%20but%20that%20there%20was%20acknowledgement%20on%20what%20kind%20of%20funding%20was%20not%20healthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20everybody%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20essentially%20spoke%20of%20the%20need%20that%20when%20they%20access%20this%20financing%20for%20their%20development%20projects%20for%20climate%20crisis%20or%20for%20energy%20transitions%2C%20it%20should%20be%20in%20a%20manner%20and%20of%20a%20kind%20that%20does%20not%20impose%20a%20debt%20burden%20on%20the%20structural%20parameters%20of%20the%20economy.%20It%20should%20be%20more%20sustainable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20session%20for%20foreign%20ministers%2C%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20there%20continued%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Ca%20resistance%20for%20a%20greater%20role%20for%20the%20global%20south%20in%20shaping%20solutions%20for%20the%20key%20issues%20of%20our%20times%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20mentioned%20that%20the%20lesson%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20perils%20of%20dependence%20for%20basic%20necessities%20on%20far%20away%20geographies%20abilities%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20economic%20concentrations%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20not%20only%20democratise%20and%20diversify%20production%2C%20but%20build%20resilient%20and%20reliable%20supply%20chains%20and%20promote%20local%20solutions.%20Only%20then%20can%20the%20global%20south%20secure%20its%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20noted%20Jaishankar.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700287920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F18114014%2Fimage-1518.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fat-indias-summit-for-global-south-leaders-raise-strong-concern-over-ongoing-conflict-in-west-asia%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20the%20second%20Voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20summit%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20referred%20to%20'new%20challenges'%20from%20the%20geopolitical%20crisis%20that%20have%20caused%20thousands%20of%20deaths%20over%20the%20last%20one%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fat-indias-summit-for-global-south-leaders-raise-strong-concern-over-ongoing-conflict-in-west-asia%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Parliament%20Panel%20Said%20on%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Bill%2C%20Which%20Seeks%20To%20Replace%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F18112028%2Fimage-1517.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20the%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20replace%20the%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%2C%201872%2C%20provides%20for%20%E2%80%9Cany%20information%E2%80%9D%20that%20is%20given%20electronically%20as%20oral%20evidence%2C%20the%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20tasked%20with%20examining%20the%20proposed%20legislation%2C%20has%20recommended%20the%20deletion%20of%20these%20words%2C%20saying%20that%20this%20could%20cause%20serious%20complications%20in%20its%20interpretations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20has%20also%20cautioned%20against%20the%20tampering%20of%20evidence%20and%20recommended%20%E2%80%9Csafeguarding%20the%20authenticity%20and%20integrity%20of%20electronic%20and%20digital%20records%20acquired%20during%20the%20course%20of%20investigation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20Bill%20(which%20seeks%20to%20replace%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%201870)%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20(which%20seeks%20to%20replace%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%2C%201973)%2C%20was%20referred%20to%20the%2031-member%20committee%20after%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsedition-law-repealed-three-new-bills-tabled-in-parliament-to-replace-criminal-laws%5C%22%3Eintroduced%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20parliament%20on%20August%2011%20by%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliamentary-panel-adopts-reports-on-three-criminal-bills-several-dissent-notes-from-opposition%5C%22%3Eadopted%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20report%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20dissent%20notes%2C%20opposition%20MPs%20have%20criticised%20these%20Bills%20for%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Flaw%2Fcriminal-bills-opposition-mp-dissent-note-hindi-imposition-copy-paste%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Ccopy-paste%E2%80%9D%20legislations%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20flagged%20drafting%20errors%20and%20the%20haste%20with%20which%20they%20are%20being%20pushed%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20analyses%20the%20main%20recommendations%20of%20the%20committee%20report%20on%20the%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Bill%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CAny%20information%E2%80%9D%20given%20electronically%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Ffiles%2Fbills_acts%2Fbills_parliament%2F2023%2FBHARATIYA_SAKSHYA_BILL%2C%25202023.pdf%5C%22%3E%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E%20defines%20evidence%20as%20oral%20and%20documentary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOral%20evidence%20includes%20%E2%80%9Cstatements%20or%20any%20information%20given%20electronically%20which%20the%20court%20permits%20or%20requires%20to%20be%20made%20before%20it%20by%20witnesses%20in%20relation%20to%20matters%20of%20fact%20under%20inquiry%20and%20such%20statements%20or%20information%E2%80%9D%2C%20while%20it%20defines%20documentary%20evidence%20as%20documents%2C%20%E2%80%9Cincluding%20electronic%20or%20digital%20records%20produced%20for%20the%20inspection%20of%20the%20court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Bill%2C%20the%20definition%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdocuments%E2%80%9D%20has%20been%20expanded%20to%20include%20electronic%20or%20digital%20records%20on%20emails%2C%20server%20logs%2C%20documents%20on%20computers%2C%20laptop%20or%20smartphone%2C%20messages%2C%20websites%2C%20locational%20evidence%20and%20voice%20mail%20messages%20stored%20on%20digital%20devices.%20The%20definition%20of%20%E2%80%9Cevidence%E2%80%9D%20has%20been%20expanded%20to%20include%20any%20information%20given%20electronically%2C%20which%20will%20enable%20the%20appearance%20of%20witnesses%2C%20accused%2C%20experts%20and%20victims%20through%20electronic%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Ffiles%2Fbills_acts%2Fbills_parliament%2F2023%2FSC_Report_Bharatiya_Sakshya_Bill_2023.pdf%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20it%20was%20brought%20to%20its%20attention%20during%20deliberations%20that%20the%20inclusion%20of%20the%20words%20%E2%80%9Cany%20information%E2%80%9D%20within%20the%20meaning%20of%20evidence%20could%20cause%20serious%20complications%20in%20its%20interpretations%2C%20and%20that%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9Cinformation%E2%80%9D%20is%20different%20from%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20has%20recommended%20that%20the%20words%20%E2%80%9Cany%20information%E2%80%9D%20be%20deleted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20committee%20opines%20that%20inclusion%20of%20%E2%80%98any%20information%E2%80%99%20along%20with%20%E2%80%98statement%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20same%20line%20may%20cause%20complications%20in%20its%20interpretation.%20The%20committee%2C%20therefore%2C%20recommends%20that%20the%20words%20%E2%80%98any%20information%E2%80%99%20may%20be%20deleted%20in%20this%20clause%20to%20avoid%20such%20complications%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-handcuffs-for-economic-offences-safeguards-electronic-evidence-misuse-parl-panel-report-on-bns%5C%22%3ENo%20Handcuffs%20for%20Economic%20Offences%2C%20Digital%20Evidence%20%E2%80%98Safeguards%E2%80%99%3A%20Parliamentary%20Panel%20Report%20on%20BNSS%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESafeguarding%20electronic%20and%20digital%20evidence%20against%20tampering%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20has%20also%20recommended%20the%20need%20to%20safeguard%20the%20authenticity%20of%20electronic%20and%20digital%20records%20acquired%20during%20investigation%20against%20tampering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20Clause%2057%20provides%20for%20treating%20electronic%20and%20digital%20records%20produced%20from%20proper%20custody%20as%20primary%20evidence%2C%20but%20does%20not%20mention%20about%20ensuring%20proper%20chain%20of%20custody%20of%20such%20digital%20and%20electronic%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20provision%20of%20maintaining%20proper%20chain%20of%20custody%20has%20already%20been%20incorporated%20within%20the%20ambit%20of%20criminal%20laws%20in%20developed%20countries%20such%20as%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%20(USA)%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20(UK).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20recommended%20that%20that%20proper%20chain%20of%20custody%20needs%20to%20be%20maintained%20to%20avoid%20tampering%20during%20the%20handling%20of%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20committee%20is%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20safeguarding%20the%20authenticity%20and%20integrity%20of%20electronic%20and%20digital%20records%20acquired%20during%20the%20course%20of%20investigation%20is%20crucial%20due%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20such%20evidences%20are%20prone%20to%20tampering%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20committee%20takes%20into%20account%20the%20suggestion%20submitted%20before%20the%20committee%20and%20recommends%20that%20a%20provision%20may%20be%20inserted%20to%20mandate%20that%20all%20electronic%20and%20digital%20records%20acquired%20as%20evidence%20during%20the%20course%20of%20investigation%20are%20securely%20handled%20and%20processed%20through%20proper%20chain%20of%20custody.%20Appropriate%20provision%20in%20this%20regard%20may%20be%20made%20in%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%2C%202023.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliamentary-panel-gender-neutrality-section-377-criminalising-adultery%5C%22%3EIn%20%E2%80%98Interest%20of%20Gender%20Neutrality%E2%80%99%2C%20Parl%20Panel%20Recommends%20Keeping%20Section%20377%2C%20Criminalising%20Adultery%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDrafting%20and%20cross-referencing%20errors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20committee%20has%20also%20noted%20a%20number%20of%20drafting%20errors%20in%20various%20clauses%20and%20recommended%20their%20rectifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20found%20several%20cross-referencing%20errors%20in%20different%20clauses%20in%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20Bill%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20committee%20also%20undertook%20a%20detailed%20examination%20of%20the%20text%20of%20each%20clause%20and%20noted%20that%20the%20Bill%20contains%20some%20cross-referencing%20errors.%20The%20committee%2C%20therefore%2C%20recommends%20the%20ministry%20to%20rectify%20such%20errors%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20concluded%20that%20the%20changes%20brought%20in%20the%20Bill%20would%20%E2%80%9Creflect%20the%20growing%20importance%20of%20digital%20evidence%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20need%20for%20a%20more%20comprehensive%20legal%20framework%20in%20line%20with%2021st%20century%20technological%20advancements%20and%20societal%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20recommendations%20on%20the%20other%20two%20Bills%20can%20be%20read%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliamentary-panel-gender-neutrality-section-377-criminalising-adultery%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-handcuffs-for-economic-offences-safeguards-electronic-evidence-misuse-parl-panel-report-on-bns%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700286898000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F18112028%2Fimage-1517.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhat-parl-panel-said-on-bharatiya-sakshya-bill-which-seeks-to-replace-the-indian-evidence-act%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Home%20Affairs%20has%20recommended%20deleting%20the%20words%20'any%20information'%20to%20avoid%20any%20misinterpretations%2C%20concerning%20electronic%20evidence%2C%20and%20ensuring%20the%20protection%20of%20digital%20evidence%20against%20tampering.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhat-parl-panel-said-on-bharatiya-sakshya-bill-which-seeks-to-replace-the-indian-evidence-act%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OpenAI%20CEO%20ouster%20followed%20disagreements%20between%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20board%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700286420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-05%2F16%2Ffull%2F1684251299-6933.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Fopenai-ceo-ouster-followed-disagreements-between-sam-altman-board-123111800180_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20disputes%20e