uction%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20utilised%20effectively.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20organised%20self-help%20groups%20to%20train%20women%20in%20creating%20bamboo%20products%2C%20which%20would%20then%20be%20sold%20nationwide.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-5-1700058095.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Namita%20has%20trained%20over%2057%20women%20from%20around%20her%20village%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-5-1700058095.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-5-1700058095-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-5-1700058095-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-5-1700058095-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-5-1700058095-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENamita%20has%20trained%20over%2057%20women%20from%20around%20her%20village.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Namita%20Namdev%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20informs%20that%20this%20Diwali%2C%20they%20sold%20more%20than%203%2C000%20bamboo%20%3Cem%3Ekandils%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9COur%20products%20are%20not%20only%20sold%20in%20India%20but%20throughout%20the%20world.%20We%20now%20have%2023%20villages%20and%20700%20women%20making%20bamboo%20products%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20products%2C%20Gaurav%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20initiative%E2%80%99s%20main%20goal%20was%20always%20to%20give%20alternative%20livelihood%20to%20tribal%20women%